simplified: A list of fixed prices for things like rooms or meals at a hotel or restaurant, or for a service from a company.

adult_definition: 'The act or result of a government requiring money for its support or for specific facilities or services.'
kids_definition: money that has to be paid as taxes
simplified: Money paid to the government for taxes and other charges.

adult_definition: 'The act of imparting knowledge or skill.'
kids_definition: the ideas of a particular person or group especially about politics religion or society that are taught to other people
simplified: The thoughts of a person or group about politics, religion, or society that are shared with others through books, speeches, or media.

adult_definition: 'Systematic knowledge of industrial processes and their application.'
kids_definition: scientific knowledge used in practical ways in industry for example in designing new machines
simplified: We use scientific knowledge to make new machines and to make things better.

adult_definition: 'A measure of cold or hot. A property that determines the direction of heat flow when an object is brought into thermal contact with other objects.'
kids_definition: the measurement in degrees of how hot or cold a thing or place is
simplified: Temperature is how hot or cold something is.

adult_definition: 'A material made of natural or man-made fibers and used for the manufacture of items such as clothing and furniture fittings.'
kids_definition: any type of cloth made by weaving or knitting
simplified: A type of cloth made by weaving or knitting.

adult_definition: 'The treatment of physical mental or social disorders or disease.'
kids_definition: the treatment of a physical problem or an illness
simplified: Doctors can help people feel better by using many ways to treat sicknesses.

adult_definition: 'The periodic rise and fall of the water resulting from gravitational interaction between the sun moon and earth.'
kids_definition: a regular rise and fall in the level of the sea caused by the pull of the moon and sun; the flow of water that happens as the sea rises and falls
simplified: The sea goes up and down because of the moon and sun, and water moves with it.

adult_definition: 'Any anuran amphibian of the family Bufonidae such as Bufo bufo of Europe. They are similar to frogs but are more terrestrial having a drier warty skin.'
kids_definition: a small animal like a frog but with a drier and less smooth skin that lives on land but breeds (= produces young) in water (= is an amphibian)
simplified: An animal called a toad lives on land, but it lays its eggs in water. When it's young, it has a long tail, but it loses it as it grows up.

adult_definition: 'The degree of danger posed by a substance to animal or plant life.'
kids_definition: the fact of being poisonous; the extent to which something is poisonous
simplified: The degree of being bad for you. Poisonousness.

adult_definition: 'Sound waves having a frequency above about 20000 hertz.'
kids_definition: sound that is higher than humans can hear
simplified: A sound too high for humans to hear comes from the art star.

adult_definition: 'The condition of being without remunerative employment.'
kids_definition: the state of not having a job
simplified: Not having a job was a hard time for him.

adult_definition: 'Any conveyance in or by which people or objects are transported.'
kids_definition: a thing that is used for transporting people or goods from one place to another such as a car or lorry
simplified: It is a thing that takes people or things from one place to another like a car or truck or train or bus or boat or plane.

adult_definition: 'Small animals and insects that can be harmful and which are difficult to control when they appear in large numbers.'
kids_definition: insects that live on the bodies of animals and sometimes humans
simplified: creatures that live on animals and people.

adult_definition: 'A periodic motion of small amplitude and high frequency characteristic of elastic bodies.'
kids_definition: a continuous shaking movement or feeling
simplified: A shaking feeling, often caused by fear, anger, or excitement.

adult_definition: 'A format or system used to record and transmit visual or audiovisual information by translating moving or still images into electrical signals.'
kids_definition: a system of recording moving pictures and sound either using a digital method of storing data or (in the past) using videotape
simplified: We can record moving pictures and sound using digital methods or old videotapes.

adult_definition: 'A list of words or phrases of a language technical field or some specialized area usually arranged in alphabetical order and often provided with brief definitions and with foreign translations.'
kids_definition: a list of words with their meanings especially in a book for learning a foreign language
simplified: A book has a list of special words and their meanings to help learn a new language.

adult_definition: 'The property of a substance or substances to convert into vapor or gas without chemical change.'
kids_definition: the quality in a substance of changing easily into a gas
simplified: Things can change into gas at a low temperature.

adult_definition: 'A conflict or a state of hostility between two or more parties nations or states in which armed forces or military operations are used.'
kids_definition: a situation in which two or more countries or groups of people fight against each other over a period of time
simplified: A war is when two or more countries or groups fight against each other for a long time.

adult_definition: 'Extravagant or useless consumption or expenditures.'
kids_definition: the fact of losing or destroying something especially because it has been used or dealt with carelessly
simplified: They broke the toy because they played with it carelessly.

adult_definition: 'An instrument of attack or defense in combat as a gun missile or sword.'
kids_definition: an object such as a knife gun bomb etc. that is used for fighting or attacking somebody
simplified: A thing like a knife, gun, or bomb that hurts people.

adult_definition: 'The day-to-day meteorological conditions especially temperature cloudiness and rainfall affecting a specific place.'
kids_definition: the condition of the atmosphere at a particular place and time such as the temperature and if there is wind rain sun etc.
simplified: The weather at a certain place and time, like how warm or cold it is and if it is sunny or rainy.

adult_definition: 'The gravitational force with which the earth attracts a body. By extension the gravitational force with which a star planet or satellite attracts a nearby body.'
kids_definition: how heavy somebody/something is which can be measured in for example kilograms or pounds
simplified: How heavy something is can be measured in pounds or kilograms.

adult_definition: 'A machine for grinding or pumping driven by a set of adjustable vanes or sails that are caused to turn by the force of the wind.'
kids_definition: a building with equipment for grinding grain into flour that is driven by the power of the wind turning long arms (called sails)
simplified: A windmill is a building with equipment that turns long arms called sails around a central post to grind grain into flour.

adult_definition: 'A wood especially when regarded as a construction material.'
kids_definition: wood that is prepared for use in building etc.
simplified: Special wood for building is called seasoned timber.

adult_definition: 'The soft curly hair that forms the fleece of sheep lamas and other animals and which is used to produce clothing.'
kids_definition: the soft hair that covers the body of sheep and some other animals
simplified: The soft hair of sheep and some animals is called wool.

adult_definition: 'A young child in the first years of life.'
kids_definition: a baby or very young child
simplified: A young child has no idea of danger and will go near anything or anyone.

adult_definition: 'Designation and reservation under a master plan of land use for light and heavy industry dwellings offices and other buildings.'
kids_definition: the practice of allowing areas of land to be used only for a particular purpose
simplified: They keep some areas of land just for one use, like protecting nature.

adult_definition: A protuberance of the Earth's crustal shell with an area of several million square miles and sufficient elevation so that much of it above sea level.
kids_definition: connected with the control of your feelings especially your desire to have sex
simplified: You need to learn how to control your emotions, especially your desire for sex and how to talk about it with others.

adult_definition: 'A narrow inlet or bay especially of the sea.'
kids_definition: a narrow area of water where the sea flows into the land
simplified: A narrow area of water where the sea and land meet.

adult_definition: 'A person firm organization etc. that provides or pledges money for an undertaking or event.'
kids_definition: the act of supporting a person organization or activity especially financially
simplified: help someone or something especially with money.

adult_definition: 'The act or fact of surviving or condition of having survived.'
kids_definition: the state of continuing to live or exist often despite difficulty or danger
simplified: It is often hard to keep going on living or existing when things are difficult or dangerous.

adult_definition: 'The cutting off or removal of dead or living parts or branches of a plant to improve shape or growth.'
kids_definition: the activity of cutting off some of the branches from a tree bush etc. so that it will grow better and stronger
simplified: Cutting some branches from a tree helps it grow better and stronger.

adult_definition: 'Provision of accommodation for rest or for residence in a room or rooms or in a dwelling place.'
kids_definition: a room or rooms in somebody else’s house that you rent to live in
simplified: A room in someone else’s house that you pay to live in.

adult_definition: 'The community or people in general or a part or section of the community grouped because of a common interest or activity.'
kids_definition: open to people in general; intended to be seen or heard by people in general
simplified: It is meant for everyone to see or hear.

adult_definition: 'A term of variable content and meaning. It may include every species of personal chattels or property. Items of merchandise supplies raw materials or finished goods. Land is excluded.'
kids_definition: things (not people) that are transported by railway or road
simplified: Things that move on trains or roads and things that don't.

adult_definition: 'A traditional or legendary story usually dealing with supernatural beings ancestors heroes or events that is with or without determinable basis of fact or a natural explanation but is used to explain some practice rite or phenomenon of nature or to justify the existence of a social institution.'
kids_definition: a story from ancient times especially one that was told to explain natural events or to describe the early history of a people; this type of story
simplified: A myth is a story from long ago that explains things in nature or tells about a people's early history.

adult_definition: 'A native or naturalized member of a state or nation who owes allegiance bears responsibilities and obtains rights including protection from the government.'
kids_definition: a person who has the legal right to belong to a particular country
simplified: A person who is a citizen of a country.

adult_definition: 'The act process or result of calculating.'
kids_definition: the act or process of using numbers to find out an amount
simplified: Counting is finding out how many things there are.

adult_definition: 'The mass of a substance per unit volume.'
kids_definition: how thick a solid liquid or gas is measured by its mass per unit of volume
simplified: We measure how thick a liquid or gas is by its weight compared to its size.

adult_definition: 'A list of record surrogates arranged in order of some attribute expressible in machine-orderable form.'
kids_definition: a list of the records in a computer file with information about where each is located
simplified: The computer keeps a list of records with information about where they are and what's in them.

adult_definition: 'The amount of change in some quantity during a time interval divided by the length of the time interval.'
kids_definition: a measurement of the number of times something happens or something does something during a particular period
simplified: The number of times something happens in a certain time.

adult_definition: 'Any rebate abatement voluntary grant of or a yielding to a demand or claim typically made by a government or controlling authority to an individual or organization.'
kids_definition: a right or an advantage that is given to a group of people an organization etc. especially by a government or an employer
simplified: A help or an advantage that a group of people gets from a government or an employer to succeed.

adult_definition: 'The rights of use over the property of someone else; a burden on a piece of land causing the owner to suffer access by another.'
kids_definition: the right to cross or use somebody’s land for a particular purpose
simplified: The right to use someone’s land is called easement.

adult_definition: 'Any act done in violation of those duties which an individual owes to the community and for the breach of which the law has provided that the offender shall make satisfaction to the public.'
kids_definition: an illegal act or activity that can be punished by law
simplified: It is against the law to do something bad and you can get in trouble for it.

adult_definition: 'A state of opposition or disagreement between ideas interests etc.'
kids_definition: a situation in which people groups or countries disagree strongly or are involved in a serious argument
simplified: A time when people or countries are very angry and disagree with each other.

adult_definition: 'The correct application of law as opposed to arbitrariness.'
kids_definition: the quality of being fair or reasonable
simplified: It is fair or reasonable to do something in a certain situation.

adult_definition: 'Designing manufacturing and utilizing physical instruments or instrument systems for detection observation measurement automatic control automatic computation communication or data processing.'
kids_definition: a set of instruments used in operating a vehicle or a machine
simplified: Tools used to run a car or a machine.

adult_definition: 'A stretch waterlogged spongy ground chiefly composed of decaying vegetable matter especially of rushes cotton grass and sphagnum moss.'
kids_definition: (an area of) wet soft ground formed of decayed (= destroyed by natural processes) plants
simplified: A swampy area with soft, wet ground where plants have decayed.

adult_definition: 'The hulk of a wrecked or stranded ship; a ship dashed against rocks or land and broken or otherwise rendered useless.'
kids_definition: a ship that has sunk or that has been very badly damaged
simplified: A ship that has sunk or is very badly damaged in a sea accident.

adult_definition: 'The science by which the properties of matter and the sources of power in nature are made useful to humans in structures machines and products.'
kids_definition: the activity of applying scientific knowledge to the design building and control of machines roads bridges electrical equipment etc.
simplified: Building and controlling machines roads bridges and electrical equipment using scientific knowledge is an activity.

adult_definition: 'An expert or official valuation.'
kids_definition: a judgement of the value performance or nature of somebody/something
simplified: A judgement about how good or bad someone/something is.

adult_definition: 'An address or form of oral communication in which a speaker makes his thoughts and emotions known before an audience often for a given purpose.'
kids_definition: a formal talk that a person gives to an audience
simplified: A person gives a formal talk to a group of people.

adult_definition: 'A treatise on a particular subject in which original research has been done in order to receive a doctoral degree.'
kids_definition: a long piece of writing completed by a student as part of a university degree based on their own research
simplified: A student finished a big writing project for their university degree that they did research for.

adult_definition: 'A group of mechanical or electrical parts or machines arranged to perform or assist a particular function.'
kids_definition: the organization or structure of something; the system for doing something
simplified: The way things are arranged or organized.

adult_definition: Compensation for the use of a person's property based on an agreed percentage of the income arising from its use.
kids_definition: a sum of money that is paid to somebody who has written a book piece of music etc. each time that it is sold or performed
simplified: Money paid to someone for using their work.

adult_definition: 'Regular allocation or deduction of money.'
kids_definition: an amount of money that can be earned or received before you start paying tax
simplified: The money you can get before you pay tax on it.

adult_definition: 'A process used to estimate an intermediate value of one (dependent) variable which is a function of a second (independent) variable when values of the dependent variable corresponding to several discrete values of the independent variable are known.'
kids_definition: the act of adding a value into a series by calculating it from surrounding known values
simplified: We add a value to a series by using the values around it.

adult_definition: 'An angular distance in degrees north or south of the equator (latitude 0°) equal to the angle subtended at the centre of the globe by the meridian between the equator and the point in question.'
kids_definition: the distance of a place north or south of the equator (= the line around the world dividing north and south) measured in degrees
simplified: The distance from the equator is measured in degrees.

adult_definition: 'The male partner in a marriage.'
kids_definition: the man that somebody is married to; a married man
simplified: A married man.

adult_definition: 'A chess piece the least valuable one.'
kids_definition: if something is in pawn it has been pawned
simplified: If it's in pawn, it's been pawned.

adult_definition: 'A branching hair-like structure that grows on the skin of birds and protects them against coldness and water and allows their wings to create lift.'
kids_definition: one of the many soft light parts covering a bird’s body
simplified: A bird has many soft light parts on its body.

adult_definition: 'A common four-legged animal (Felis silvestris) that is often kept as a household pet.'
kids_definition: a small animal with soft fur that people often keep as a pet. Cats catch and kill birds and mice.
simplified: A cat is a small animal with soft fur. It catches birds and mice. Cats are good at climbing and jumping. They have four legs and a long tail.

adult_definition: 'Of a physical object having great weight.'
kids_definition: falling or hitting something with a lot of force
simplified: hit very hard.

adult_definition: 'Not large or big; small in size.'
kids_definition: not as big as something else of the same kind
simplified: It was not as big as the other one.

adult_definition: 'Thick strong string made of several strands that have been twisted together.'
kids_definition: a number of similar things attached together by a string or thread
simplified: Many similar things tied with a string.

adult_definition: 'A large organ in the body that stores and metabolizes nutrients destroys toxins and produces bile. Responsible for thousands of biochemical reactions.'
kids_definition: a large organ in the body that cleans the blood and produces bile
simplified: The liver is a part of the body that cleans the blood and makes bile.

adult_definition: 'The period between sunset and sunrise when a location faces far away from the sun thus when the sky is dark.'
kids_definition: the time between one day and the next when it is dark when people usually sleep
simplified: The night when people sleep.

adult_definition: 'Not rough; having a surface texture that lacks friction.'
kids_definition: completely flat and even without any rough areas or holes
simplified: The ground was flat and smooth, but still had rough spots in some places.

adult_definition: 'What person or people; which person or people.'
kids_definition: used to show which person or people you mean
simplified: To show which person you mean.

adult_definition: 'Relatively large distance from one surface to the opposite in its smallest solid dimension.'
kids_definition: having a larger distance between opposite sides or surfaces than other similar objects or than normal
simplified: Things that are wider or bigger than usual on opposite sides.

adult_definition: 'The lower part of the front of the torso (or a comparable part of an animal) confined by the upper side by the midriff and the lowerside by the pelvis. Contains the intestines.'
kids_definition: the part of the body below the chest
simplified: The middle part of the body has a tummy and guts.

adult_definition: To produce harmonious sounds with one's voice.
kids_definition: to make musical sounds with your voice in the form of a song or tune
simplified: To sing a song.

adult_definition: 'A musical part or section that is higher than alto and all other sections with a typical range from the A below middle C to high C (two octaves above middle C).'
kids_definition: a singing voice with the highest range for a woman or boy; a singer with a soprano voice
simplified: A voice that sings very high is called a soprano.

adult_definition: 'A musical part or section higher than tenor but lower than soprano with a typical range from the F below middle C to the E a tenth above it.'
kids_definition: a musical part that is written for an alto voice
simplified: A musical part written for a high female voice.

adult_definition: 'Expression of greeting used by two or more people who meet each other.'

simplified: The pain in my head was sharp and piercing and felt like it was coming from the back of my head and spreading all over.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after ten and before twelve represented in Roman numerals as XI in Arabic numerals as 11.'
kids_definition: a team of eleven players for football (soccer) cricket or hockey
simplified: A group of eleven people playing football, cricket, or hockey is called an eleven.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after fourteen and before sixteen represented in Roman numerals as XV and in Arabic numerals as 15.'
kids_definition: a team of Rugby Union players
simplified: Rugby players from four countries played a charity match.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after nineteen and before twenty-one represented in Roman numerals as XX and in Arabic numerals as 20.'
kids_definition: numbers years or temperatures from 20 to 29
simplified: The temperature went from 20 to 29 in the morning and 28 in the afternoon.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after thirty-nine and before forty-one represented in Roman numerals as XL and in Arabic numerals as 40.'
kids_definition: numbers years or temperatures from 40 to 49
simplified: We used temperatures from 40 to 49 degrees Fahrenheit to decide if it was a hot day.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after forty-nine and before fifty-one represented in Roman numerals as L and in Arabic numerals as 50.'
kids_definition: numbers years or temperatures from 50 to 59
simplified: The temperatures from 50 to 59 degrees Fahrenheit showed the weather.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after fifty-nine and before sixty-one represented in Roman numerals as LX and in Arabic numerals as 60.'
kids_definition: numbers years or temperatures from 60 to 69
simplified: Numbers from 60 to 69 are also given, so children can work out the answer alone.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after sixty-nine and before seventy-one represented in Roman numerals as LXX and in Arabic numerals as 70.'
kids_definition: numbers years or temperatures from 70 to 79
simplified: When it is between 70 and 79 degrees Fahrenheit and the air is between 50 and 60 percent humid, we need to take care so mold doesn't grow.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after seventy-nine and before eighty-one represented in Roman numerals as LXXX and in Arabic numerals as 80.'
kids_definition: numbers years or temperatures from 80 to 89
simplified: It will take 7 to 10 days of temperatures between 80 and 89 degrees Fahrenheit to wake up the seeds.

adult_definition: 'The cardinal number occurring after eighty-nine and before ninety-one represented in Roman numerals as XC and in Arabic numerals as 90.'
kids_definition: numbers years or temperatures from 90 to 99
simplified: Very high temperatures are from 90 to 99.

adult_definition: 'A person that someone has met repeatedly and has a superficial knowledge of.'
kids_definition: a person that you know but who is not a close friend
simplified: A person you know who is not a close friend is called an acquaintance.

adult_definition: 'To complain or protest in an excessive annoying or persistent way.'
kids_definition: to make a long high unpleasant sound because you are in pain or unhappy
simplified: to make a loud unhappy noise because you hurt.

adult_definition: 'The female leader of a city or municipality.'
kids_definition: the wife of a mayor or a woman who helps a mayor at official ceremonies
simplified: The mayor's wife or a woman who helps the mayor.

adult_definition: 'The general perceptual behaviour and the specific responses made in relation to sound stimuli.'
kids_definition: an official meeting at which the facts about a crime complaint etc. are presented to the person or group of people who will have to decide what action to take
simplified: A meeting where the facts about a crime are told to the people who decide what to do.

adult_definition: 'A set of instructions (typically consisting of ingredients and a method) for creating something (usually a food product or dish).'
kids_definition: a set of instructions that tells you how to cook something and the ingredients (= items of food) you need for it
simplified: A recipe is a list of things you need and what to do with them to make a dish.

adult_definition: 'An explanation of something that is not immediately obvious.'
kids_definition: the particular way in which something is understood or explained
simplified: The special way something is explained.

adult_definition: 'The sickness nausea and headaches that occur the morning after a person drinks too much alcohol.'
kids_definition: the headache and sick feeling that you have the day after drinking too much alcohol
simplified: The sick feeling you get the morning after you drink too much.

adult_definition: 'At a more advanced or later point in a trajectory (such as a journey).'
kids_definition: at or to a greater distance in space or time
simplified: far away from a certain point or time.

adult_definition: 'An agglomeration of ice crystals falling from the sky.'
kids_definition: a small soft piece of frozen water that falls from the sky as snow
simplified: Snow is small soft pieces of frozen water that fall from the sky.

adult_definition: 'To have a strong desire for something.'
kids_definition: to feel sexual desire for somebody
simplified: to feel love for someone.

adult_definition: 'The way words are made to sound when spoken.'
kids_definition: the way in which a particular person pronounces the words of a language
simplified: The way someone says words is how they sound when they say them.

adult_definition: 'The process of making woven material on a loom'
kids_definition: the activity of making cloth by weaving
simplified: Making cloth by weaving or knitting yarn, thread, or other material is an activity.

adult_definition: 'Something understood and retained in the mind from experience reasoning or/and imagination; a generalisation (generic basic form) or abstraction (mental impression) of a particular set of instances or occurances.'
kids_definition: an idea or a principle that is connected with something abstract
simplified: A thought or rule that is part of a bigger idea or plan.

adult_definition: 'A single formed character or symbol usually representing a letter in a font'
kids_definition: a symbol or picture that represents a word especially one from an ancient writing system
simplified: A symbol that stands for a word from an old writing system.

adult_definition: 'A work that was written by hand.'
kids_definition: a very old book or document that was written by hand before printing was invented
simplified: An old book or paper written by hand before printing began.

adult_definition: 'Either of two species of bird in the family Meleagrididae with fan-shaped tail and wattled neck.'
kids_definition: a large bird that is often kept for its meat eaten especially at Christmas in the UK and at Thanksgiving in the US
simplified: A turkey is a big bird that people often eat at special times like Christmas and Thanksgiving.

adult_definition: 'A group of vehicles or ships travelling in formation for mutual support such as resisting attacks by an enemy.'
kids_definition: a group of vehicles or ships travelling together especially when soldiers or other vehicles travel with them for protection
simplified: Many vehicles or ships travel together, like when soldiers go with them to keep them safe.

adult_definition: 'Transportation and/or handing over of ordered goods to the orderer.'
kids_definition: the act of taking goods letters etc. to the people they have been sent to
simplified: Sending letters and things to the people they are meant for through the mail system.

adult_definition: 'Caring for horses or other animals by brushing and cleaning them.'
kids_definition: the things that you do to keep your clothes and hair clean and neat or to keep an animal’s fur or hair clean
simplified: The things we do to keep our clothes and hair clean and neat are called grooming habits.

adult_definition: '(Of a person or animal) Narrow in size and usually indicating carrying little fat.'
kids_definition: very thin especially in a way that you find unpleasant or ugly
simplified: It is very thin in a way that you don't like.

adult_definition: 'The property of being thin.'
kids_definition: the fact of not having much fat or muscle on your body
simplified: Having little fat or muscle on your body makes you look slim.

adult_definition: 'The property of being thin.'
kids_definition: the quality in a person of not having much fat; the quality of being thin and fit
simplified: The quality of being thin and fit.

adult_definition: 'The quality of being patient.'
kids_definition: the quality of being extremely patient and not complaining
simplified: Being very patient and not complaining when things are hard or hurt.

adult_definition: 'The principal character in a work of fiction.'
kids_definition: the main character in a play film or book

adult_definition: 'The science dealing with the origin and historical development of words.'
kids_definition: the study of the origin and history of words and their meanings
simplified: Studying how words came to be and what they mean is a very interesting and complicated subject that needs a lot of knowledge about languages, old books, and history.

adult_definition: 'Containing comprising or made from.'
kids_definition: relating to or showing somebody/something

adult_definition: 'To attack by using one or more bombs.'
kids_definition: to attack a place by firing large guns at it or dropping bombs on it continuously
simplified: The soldiers kept firing big guns and dropping bombs on the place for a long time to destroy it completely.

adult_definition: 'Originally a container especially for a relic and often a cult image and/or a holy or sacred place containing the same.'
kids_definition: a place where people come to worship because it is connected with a holy person or event

adult_definition: 'A part of the body of a saint or something that was owned by a saint kept for veneration.'
kids_definition: a part of the body or clothing of a holy person or something that they owned that is kept after their death and respected as a religious object

adult_definition: 'A situation that constitutes an immediate risk for injury on a person or property.'
kids_definition: a person or thing that may cause damage or harm somebody

adult_definition: 'Seat for more than one person narrow and long with or without back support made of hard materials (wood metal) that is normally found in public places (churches parks etc.).'
kids_definition: a long seat for two or more people usually made of wood

adult_definition: 'A professional who designs buildings or other structures or who prepares plans and superintends construction.'
kids_definition: a person who designs or puts together a program or computer system
simplified: A person who makes a computer program or system.

adult_definition: 'The largest of the great apes (Hominidae) native to the forests of central Africa.'
kids_definition: a very large powerful African ape (= an animal like a large monkey without a tail) covered with black or brown hair
simplified: A large powerful ape lived in the jungle of Africa.

adult_definition: 'A person trained to compete in sports.'
kids_definition: a person who is good at sports and physical exercise
simplified: A person good at sports will have less fat.

adult_definition: 'A person who exhibits and executes a skill or talent (often in music or drama) in front of an audience in order to entertain them.'
kids_definition: a person who performs for an audience in a show concert etc.

adult_definition: 'To examine by asking (a witness for example).'
kids_definition: to obtain information from a computer or other machine

adult_definition: 'That which one is morally or legally obligated to do.'
kids_definition: something that you feel you have to do because it is your moral or legal responsibility

adult_definition: 'One of the four principal compass points specifically 270° conventionally directed to the left on maps. The direction of the setting sun.'
kids_definition: the direction that you look towards to see the sun go down; one of the four main points of the compass
simplified: The direction you look to see the sun go down; one of the four main points of the compass.

adult_definition: 'Person who wrote the content of a published novel book or text.'
kids_definition: a person who writes books or the person who wrote a particular book

adult_definition: 'Person who wrote the content of a published novel book or text.'
kids_definition: a person whose job is writing books stories articles etc.
simplified: A person who writes books, stories, and articles will always help with writing.

adult_definition: 'The series of actions situations and events that make up a novel or story.'
kids_definition: the series of events that form the story of a novel play film etc.
simplified: The story is made up of many things that happen.

adult_definition: 'The switch between a ruled death sentence and a milder one.'
kids_definition: an event or a situation to be grateful for usually because it stops something unpleasant

adult_definition: 'A disorderly and often noisy group of people.'
kids_definition: a large group of noisy people who are or may become violent

adult_definition: 'A words or formula supposed to have magical powers.'
kids_definition: the state of being under a magic spell
simplified: Being under a magic spell was not nice.

adult_definition: 'Having fear of or for something.'
kids_definition: feeling fear; frightened because you think that you might be hurt or suffer
simplified: You feel afraid or worried that something bad might happen.

adult_definition: To cut the head from a person's body.
kids_definition: to cut off somebody’s head
simplified: The king's order must have been given when he was very angry or hated someone.

adult_definition: 'A meal that is eaten in the late afternoon or evening daily.'
kids_definition: the main meal of the day eaten either in the middle of the day or in the evening
simplified: The main meal of the day had meat or fish with vegetables and sometimes dessert.

adult_definition: 'A contraceptive device consisting of a thin rubber or latex sheath worn over the penis during intercourse.'
kids_definition: a thin rubber tube that a man wears over his penis during sex to stop a woman from becoming pregnant or to protect against disease
simplified: A thin tube that men wear to stop pregnancy or protect against disease.

adult_definition: 'A unit of length equal to 2.54 centimetres.'
kids_definition: a unit for measuring length or height equal to 2.54 centimetres. There are 12 inches in a foot.
simplified: There are inches in a foot, feet in a yard, and yards in a mile.

adult_definition: 'Of relating to or containing an alkali.'
kids_definition: having the nature of an alkali

adult_definition: 'A journey made to a sacred place or a religious journey.'
kids_definition: a journey to a holy place for religious reasons
simplified: A special trip to a sacred place for worship.

adult_definition: 'To suffer the loss of something by wrongdoing or non-compliance.'
kids_definition: to lose or give something up as a necessary consequence of something that you have done

adult_definition: 'An official appointed to rule on plays and procedure.'
kids_definition: a person who is asked to settle an argument

adult_definition: 'A simple accessory that can be attached to clothing with a pin or fastener often round and bearing a design logo or message and used for decoration identification or to show political affiliation etc.'
kids_definition: a small piece of metal or plastic with a design or words on it that a person wears or carries to show that they belong to an organization support something have achieved something have a particular rank etc.
simplified: A small piece of metal or plastic with a design or words on it that a person wears or carries to show they belong to a group or support something.

adult_definition: 'Many times with short intervals between occasions.'
kids_definition: usually; in a way that is typical of somebody/something

adult_definition: 'A specific radio frequency or band of frequencies used for transmitting television.'
kids_definition: a band of radio waves used for making television or radio broadcasts
simplified: Radio waves are used for TV and radio broadcasts.

adult_definition: 'Number of occurrences of a repeated event per unit of time (e. g. oscillations per second).'
kids_definition: the rate at which a sound or electromagnetic wave vibrates (= moves up and down)
simplified: The number of times a sound or wave goes up and down in a second.

adult_definition: 'Using the right hand more skillfully than the left hand.'
kids_definition: a right-handed tool is designed to be used with the right hand
simplified: A tool for the right hand is designed to be used that way.

adult_definition: 'An event organized to discuss an issue with a range of speakers.'
kids_definition: a large official meeting usually lasting for a few days at which people with the same work or interests come together to discuss their views
simplified: A big meeting where people with the same job or interests come together to talk about their ideas and share what they know.

adult_definition: 'A meeting held for the exchange of useful information by members of a community.'
kids_definition: a meeting for discussion or training
simplified: We have a talk to learn something.

adult_definition: 'A state in which a group of people is continuously making silly jokes that can nevertheless lead to laughing fits as a reaction. Under the right circumstances the state can maintain itself or be induced in others contageously. The use of weed (Cannabis sativa) promotes the state in some individuals but it can also be induced by a joke or reference to an (earlier) funny event.'
kids_definition: making you feel as if you are about to fall
simplified: You feel sleepy, then wake up and are somewhere else.

adult_definition: 'A whirlwind whirlpool or similarly moving matter in the form of a spiral or column.'
kids_definition: a mass of air water etc. that turns round and round very fast and pulls things into its centre
simplified: A big whirlpool that moves very quickly and pulls things towards its middle.

adult_definition: 'The area encompassing the upper thigh hip and buttocks on one side of a human primate or quadruped animal especially one that is able to sit on its hindquarters.'
kids_definition: the tops of the legs and buttocks; the similar parts at the back of the body of an animal that has four legs
simplified: The top parts of the legs and bottom; the same parts on an animal's back.

adult_definition: 'A morpheme that is placed at the start of a word.'
kids_definition: a letter or group of letters added to the beginning of a word to change its meaning such as un- in unhappy and pre- in preheat
simplified: A prefix is a letter or group of letters added to the beginning of a word to change its meaning.

adult_definition: 'A large heavy body which does not produce energy by nuclear fusion moving in a stable elliptical orbit around a star.'
kids_definition: a large round object in space that moves around a star (such as the sun) and receives light from it
simplified: A planet is a big thing in space that goes around a star like the sun and gets light from it.

adult_definition: 'A short account of an incident often humorous.'
kids_definition: a short interesting or funny story about a real person or event

adult_definition: 'A period of 1000 years.'
kids_definition: a period of 1 000 years especially as calculated before or after the birth of Christ
simplified: A long time of 1 000 years, around Christ’s birth, is often used to describe things that happened then.

adult_definition: 'Engaged in or ready for military or naval operations.'
kids_definition: the activity of being involved in a battle against an enemy

adult_definition: 'A domesticated animal Equus asinus.'
kids_definition: an animal of the horse family with short legs and long ears. People ride donkeys or use them to carry heavy loads.
simplified: Donkeys are animals from the horse family with short legs and long ears. We ride them or use them to carry heavy loads.

adult_definition: 'A measure taken beforehand to ward off evil or secure good or success.'
kids_definition: something that is done in advance in order to prevent problems or to avoid danger
simplified: Something that helps us avoid trouble before it happens.

adult_definition: 'Diurnal bird of prey belonging to the Accipitridae family.'
kids_definition: a large European bird of prey (= a bird that kills other creatures for food) of the hawk family
simplified: A large European bird of prey with a rounded tail and broad wings.

adult_definition: 'To have problems articulating the words repeting sometimes some syllables.'
kids_definition: to speak in a way that shows that you are not confident

adult_definition: 'To have problems articulating the words repeting sometimes some syllables.'
kids_definition: to have difficulty speaking because you cannot stop yourself from repeating the first sound of some words several times
simplified: If you have trouble talking because you repeat the first sound of some words, you have this difficulty.

adult_definition: 'The massive positively charged central part of an atom made up of protons and neutrons.'
kids_definition: the part of an atom that contains most of its mass and that carries a positive electric charge
simplified: The middle part of an atom is heavy and has a positive charge.

adult_definition: 'To emit or lose blood.'
kids_definition: to lose blood especially from a wound or an injury

adult_definition: 'A beast of burden much used in desert areas of the genus Camelus.'
kids_definition: an animal with a long neck and one or two humps on its back used in desert countries for riding on or for carrying goods
simplified: A camel is an animal with a long neck and humps on its back that people ride or use to carry things in the desert.

adult_definition: 'The act for living things of moving from one biome to another.'
kids_definition: the movement every year of large numbers of birds or animals from one place to another

adult_definition: 'Any of various edible fungi of the genus Tuber that grow in the soil.'
kids_definition: an expensive type of fungus that grows underground used in cooking

adult_definition: 'A tree of the genus Ulmus of the family Ulmaceae large deciduous trees with alternate stipulate leaves and small apetalous flowers.'
kids_definition: a tall tree with broad leaves
simplified: A big tree with wide leaves stood in the forest.

adult_definition: 'A woman who has never had sexual intercourse.'
kids_definition: a person who has never had sex
simplified: A person who has never had sex is called a virgin.

adult_definition: 'One of the four principal compass points specifically 90° conventionally directed to the right on maps. The direction of the rising sun.'
kids_definition: the direction that you look towards to see the sun rise; one of the four main points of the compass
simplified: The way you look to see the sun come up; one of the four main points on a map.

adult_definition: 'A crime less serious than a felony.'
kids_definition: an act of breaking a law or rule

adult_definition: 'A prolonged military assault on a blockade of a city or fortress with the intent of conquering by force or attrition.'
kids_definition: surrounded by an army or the police in a siege

adult_definition: 'Species of feline (Puma concolor) tawny-colored with black-tipped ears and tail.'
kids_definition: a large American wild animal of the cat family with yellow-brown or grey fur
simplified: A big cat with yellow-brown or grey fur and a long tail with a black tip lives in the western and central parts of North America.

adult_definition: All coverings designed to be worn on a person's body.
kids_definition: the things that you wear such as trousers dresses and jackets

adult_definition: 'Contrary to reason or propriety.'
kids_definition: things that are or that seem to be absurd

adult_definition: 'Marked by extreme and violent energy.'
kids_definition: showing strong feelings or a lot of activity often in a way that is violent

adult_definition: 'Mentally ill; affected with madness or insanity.'
kids_definition: having a mental illness that makes somebody unable to think or behave normally

adult_definition: 'In a manner contrary to law.'
kids_definition: without having permission or approval from somebody in authority

adult_definition: 'The weighted average life of a security.'
kids_definition: the length of time that something lasts or continues
simplified: How long something lasts.

adult_definition: 'In a state of satisfaction.'
kids_definition: believing or accepting that something is true

adult_definition: 'The body of customary beliefs social forms and material traits constituting a distinct complex of tradition of a racial or social group.'
kids_definition: the customs and beliefs art way of life and social organization of a particular country or group

kids_definition: the action of giving up the position of being king or queen

adult_definition: 'The quality or state of being silly.'

adult_definition: 'An act of the sovereign power granting a pardon.'

adult_definition: 'An interjection of gratitude or politeness used in response to something done or given.'

adult_definition: 'An animal killed by traffic.'
kids_definition: the killing of an animal by a car hitting it on the road

kids_definition: a statement or piece of writing that tells you how something works or makes something easier to understand

kids_definition: that you can touch or feel

adult_definition: 'Involving the entire earth; not limited or provincial in scope.'
kids_definition: covering or affecting the whole world

kids_definition: the activity of making these designs drawings or pictures or the use of these images

adult_definition: 'The abstract property of a human of living in a specific area given by precise and well defined borders. (This may be part of or include citizenship but not necessarily so e.g. for people having several places of residence for foreigners or ones officially being accepted on long-term transient living terms)'

kids_definition: a belief or set of beliefs held and taught by a Church a political party etc.
