simplified: The two soft edges at the valley's mouth would have been better for the little prince.

adult_definition: 'Volume of something how large it is.'
kids_definition: the fact of being big in size or quantity
simplified: Being big in size or quantity is a fact.

adult_definition: 'A government with a hereditary head of state.'
kids_definition: a system of government by a king or a queen
simplified: A king or queen, or a group of people, make laws and decisions for a country.

adult_definition: 'To engage in plotting or enter into a conspiracy.'
kids_definition: to secretly plan with other people to do something illegal or harmful
simplified: To make a secret plan with others to do something bad.

adult_definition: 'Collective violent action against an established power or arbitrary authority.'
kids_definition: opposition to authority within an organization a political party etc.
simplified: When people in a group, like a party, don't follow the rules, it can cause big problems.

adult_definition: 'To declare after a judgement that somebody is guilty of commiting a crime.'
kids_definition: to show or suggest that somebody is guilty of something
simplified: It shows that someone did something bad.

adult_definition: 'The mark or visible sign left by something which is lost has perished or is no longer present.'
kids_definition: a small part of something that still exists after the rest of it has stopped existing
simplified: A little bit of something that is still here after everything else is gone.

adult_definition: 'A person appointed to a high office in the government.'
kids_definition: a senior member of the government who is in charge of a government department or a branch of one
simplified: A high-up person in the government who is in charge of a part of it.

adult_definition: 'A payment to a remote recipient.'
kids_definition: the act of sending money to somebody in order to pay for something
simplified: He sent money to buy things.

adult_definition: 'The fruit of a small citrus tree (Citrus reticulata) resembling the orange.'
kids_definition: a type of small orange with loose skin that comes off easily
simplified: A little orange with loose skin that peels easily.

adult_definition: 'Period of time when a person is a child.'
kids_definition: the period of somebody’s life when they are a child
simplified: The time when someone is a child.

adult_definition: 'An organ in the body that produces urine.'
kids_definition: either of the two organs in the body that remove waste products from the blood and produce urine
simplified: Kidneys are the two organs that clean the blood and make urine.

adult_definition: 'A dried seed fruit root bark or vegetative substance used in nutritionally insignificant quantities as a food additive for the purpose of flavoring.'
kids_definition: one of the various types of powder or seed that come from plants and are used in cooking. Spices have a strong taste and smell.
simplified: Spices come from plants and have a strong taste and smell. They are used in cooking to add flavor to food.

adult_definition: 'The quality of being beautiful.'
kids_definition: the quality of giving pleasure to the senses or to the mind
simplified: Something that is pleasing to the senses or mind, especially in a gentle or sophisticated way.

adult_definition: 'One whom another follows or comes after in any office or position.'
kids_definition: a thing such as a machine that has been followed or replaced by something else
simplified: Some things, like old machines, are forgotten when they are replaced.

adult_definition: 'The feeling of having confidence restored.'
kids_definition: the fact of giving advice or help that takes away a person’s fears or doubts
simplified: Giving advice or help can make people feel more confident and comfortable.

adult_definition: 'The edible fruit of the cucumber plant having a green rind and crisp white flesh.'
kids_definition: a long vegetable with dark green skin that is light green inside usually eaten raw
simplified: It is a type of vegetable with dark green skin and light green inside, often eaten raw in salads.

adult_definition: '(arithmetic) the mathematical operation of increasing one amount by another. The result of adding two quantities is their sum.'
kids_definition: the process of adding two or more numbers together to find their total
simplified: Counting two or more numbers to find the answer.

adult_definition: 'A series of holes created to facilitate the separation of two or more parts.'
kids_definition: the process of splitting or tearing in such a way that a hole is left
simplified: This is when something tears apart, leaving a hole.

adult_definition: 'A group of people authorised to represent a person or organisation.'
kids_definition: a group of people who represent the views of an organization a country etc.
simplified: A group of people who speak for others.

adult_definition: 'To acquire or attempt to acquire knowledge or an ability to do something.'
kids_definition: to gain knowledge or skill by studying from experience from being taught etc.
simplified: to learn by doing, being taught, and seeing.

adult_definition: 'A nightclub where dancing takes place.'
kids_definition: a club party or event where people dance to recorded pop music
simplified: A party where people dance to pop music.

adult_definition: 'To beset or surround with armed forces for the purpose of compelling to surrender.'
kids_definition: to surround a building city etc. with soldiers until the people inside are forced to let you in
simplified: A king surrounds a city with soldiers until the people inside let him in.

adult_definition: 'Meant to be kept secret within a certain circle of persons; not intended to be known publicly.'
kids_definition: meant to be kept secret and not told to or shared with other people
simplified: It is a secret and nobody should tell it to others.

adult_definition: 'A strip of land kept clear and set aside for airplanes to take off from and land on.'
kids_definition: a long narrow piece of ground with a hard surface that an aircraft takes off from and lands on
simplified: A runway is a long narrow piece of ground with a hard surface where an airplane takes off and lands.

adult_definition: 'Physics: Measure of the degree to which an object (e. g. electronic part wire) opposes the passage of an electric current.'
kids_definition: the opposition of a substance or device to the flow of an electrical current
simplified: The thing that stops electricity from flowing.

adult_definition: 'A large wild canid (Canidae) closely related to the dog.'
kids_definition: a large wild animal of the dog family that lives and hunts in groups
simplified: A wolf is a big wild dog that lives and hunts with its friends.

adult_definition: 'A decorative ball of fluff.'
kids_definition: a small ball made of wool used for decoration especially on a hat
simplified: A small ball made of wool is used for decoration, especially on a hat.

adult_definition: 'A person who is addicted to drinking alcohol excessively.'
kids_definition: a person who drinks a lot of alcohol
simplified: People who drink a lot of alcohol might get sick with liver disease.

adult_definition: 'School for children from three to six years old.'
kids_definition: nursery school (= a school for children between the ages of about two and five)
simplified: We go to a special school for little children to learn and play.

adult_definition: 'The state of emotions of a person to whom something irreversible happened that leads to a feeling of sadness or regret; most often occurring e.g. after a beloved one died or a long relationship split up.'
kids_definition: clothes that people wear to show that they are sad at somebody’s death
simplified: The clothes people wear when someone dies.

adult_definition: 'A length of intestine stuffed with ground (organ) meat and other ingredients. Instead of intestines a different kind of wrapper can be used.'
kids_definition: a mixture of meat fat bread etc. cut into small pieces put into a long tube of skin cooked and eaten whole or served cold in thin slices
simplified: People cook a mixture of meat, fat, and bread, cut it into small pieces, put it in a long skin tube, and eat it whole or slice it thin and serve it cold.

adult_definition: 'A ceremony to bury or cremate a deceased person.'
kids_definition: a ceremony often a religious one for burying or cremating (= burning) a dead person
simplified: A special event, often a religious one, to say goodbye to someone who has died, especially in a war.

adult_definition: 'Strong black coffee brewed by forcing hot water under pressure through finely ground coffee beans.'
kids_definition: strong black coffee made by forcing steam or boiling water through ground coffee
simplified: We make strong black coffee by pouring hot water through ground coffee beans in a special pot.

adult_definition: 'The quality or condition of a need for immediate attention.'
kids_definition: the quality of needing to be dealt with or happen immediately
simplified: Something that must be done right away, like an emergency.

adult_definition: 'The loss of a ship in sea because of an accident.'
kids_definition: the loss or destruction of a ship at sea because of a storm or because it hits rocks etc.
simplified: The ship sank because of a big storm or hitting rocks.

adult_definition: 'Acephalous marine mollusk with an irregular bivalve shell.'
kids_definition: a large flat shellfish. Some types of oyster can be eaten and others produce shiny white jewels called pearls.
simplified: Some types of shellfish called oysters can be eaten or make white jewels called pearls.

adult_definition: 'Person whose job is to wear clothes in order to present them.'
kids_definition: a person whose job is to wear and display new styles of clothes
simplified: A person who wears and shows new clothes.

adult_definition: 'In an acoustic manner or using an acoustic musical instrument.'
kids_definition: using musical instruments that make sound naturally not using electrical equipment
simplified: We play traditional folk music with instruments that make sound on their own, not with electric equipment.

adult_definition: 'A nutlike fruit from the plant Arachis hypogaea that grows on long stems under ground.'
kids_definition: an offensive word for a person who you think is stupid
simplified: a bad word for someone you think is silly.

adult_definition: 'A female person that plays a designated role in a film or play.'
kids_definition: a woman who performs on the stage on television or in films especially as a profession
simplified: A woman who acts on stage, TV or in movies as a job.

adult_definition: 'The cut made in a field by a plough.'
kids_definition: a long narrow cut in the ground especially one made by a plough for planting seeds in
simplified: A long, narrow hole in the ground, like one made by a plough for putting seeds in a field.

adult_definition: 'An outer garment covering the upper torso and arms.'
kids_definition: a piece of outdoor clothing that is worn over other clothes to keep warm or dry. Coats have sleeves (= parts covering the arms) and may be long or short.
simplified: A coat is a piece of clothing that you wear over other clothes to keep warm or dry. It has sleeves and may be long or short.

adult_definition: 'The transport and movement of goods people and animals over water.'
kids_definition: the activity of carrying people or goods from one place to another by ship or by some other means
simplified: Moving people or things from one place to another by ship or other means.

adult_definition: 'A title of respect used when addressing a man sometimes with a surname added.'
kids_definition: used especially by children to address a man whose name they do not know
simplified: You use "sir" when you don't know a man's name, especially kids.

adult_definition: 'A snack made of various ingredients (typically meat cheese and condiments) placed between two slices of bread.'
kids_definition: two slices of bread often spread with butter with a layer of meat cheese etc. between them
simplified: We often put butter on two slices of bread with meat, cheese, etc., in between.

adult_definition: 'A tool for felling trees or chopping wood consisting of a heavy most commonly metallic head flattened to a blade on one side and which is attached to a usually wooden handle.'
kids_definition: a tool with a wooden handle and a heavy metal blade used for cutting up wood cutting down trees etc.
simplified: An axe has a wooden handle and a heavy metal blade to cut wood or trees.

adult_definition: 'One more in addition to the current one.'
kids_definition: one more; an extra thing or person
simplified: One more; something extra to make things better.

adult_definition: 'By the length; in a line with the length; lengthwise.'
kids_definition: in a line that follows the side of something long
simplified: Along a long, narrow path, like a road or a river, from one place to another.

adult_definition: 'Of high or especially quick cognitive capacity.'
kids_definition: good at learning understanding and thinking in a logical way about things; showing this ability
simplified: good at learning and thinking logically in school and activities.

adult_definition: 'To bring peace to a place or situation.'
kids_definition: to bring peace to an area where there is fighting or a war
simplified: To bring peace to a place where people are fighting.

adult_definition: 'To bring peace to a place or situation.'
kids_definition: to make a tense or painful part of your body feel more comfortable
simplified: To make a part of your body feel better or to make someone happy.

adult_definition: 'Not giving sufficient attention or thought especially concerning the avoidance of harm or mistakes.'
kids_definition: not giving enough attention and thought to what you are doing so that you make mistakes
simplified: You are not thinking about what you are doing, so you make mistakes and waste time.

adult_definition: 'Requiring little skill or effort; posing no difficulty.'
kids_definition: not difficult; done or obtained without a lot of effort or problems
simplified: The thing was not hard to do.

adult_definition: 'Not any of previously mentioned things.'
kids_definition: not one of a group of people or things; not any
simplified: Not one of them.

adult_definition: 'Not where something or someone usually is.'
kids_definition: used to say that a particular situation no longer exists
simplified: They used to say that something was no longer happening or true.

adult_definition: 'The lunar phase between new moon and full moon during which only half of the moon is visible.'
kids_definition: the moon when only half of it can be seen from the earth; the time when this happens
simplified: The moon when we can see only half of it is called a quarter moon.

adult_definition: 'A favorable circumstance or occasion.'
kids_definition: a suitable time or situation when you have the opportunity to do something
simplified: A good time to do what you want to do.

adult_definition: 'A favorable circumstance or occasion.'
kids_definition: a thing that may happen or be true; the fact that something might happen or be true but is not certain
simplified: It could happen or be true, but we are not sure.

adult_definition: 'To do something well; to distinguish oneself.'
kids_definition: to do extremely well and even better than you usually do
simplified: To do very well takes a lot of courage.

adult_definition: 'To pass on knowledge and skills.'
kids_definition: to teach students only what is necessary in order to pass a particular test rather than help them develop a range of skills
simplified: The teacher only taught what was needed to pass the test, not how to understand the subject.

adult_definition: 'An object designed for amusement or play usually intended for children to use.'
kids_definition: an object for children to play with
simplified: A toy is highly recommended but not necessary for the success of the story.

adult_definition: 'It is hoped that; I hope.'
kids_definition: used to express what you hope will happen
simplified: I hope something good will happen or I think something good will happen soon.

adult_definition: 'The currency of the European Monetary Union with symbol €.'
kids_definition: the unit of money of some countries of the European Union
simplified: The money unit in some European countries is the euro.

adult_definition: 'Group of words whose meaning is different from the sum of its parts.'
kids_definition: a group of words that have a particular meaning when used together
simplified: (Cannot be provided without the original sentence)

adult_definition: 'An old English unit of volume equal to about nine Imperial gallons when dealing with beer/ale and one third of a tun when dealing with wine.'
kids_definition: a unit for measuring volume equal to about 41 litres
simplified: A unit that measures volume, about 41 litres.

adult_definition: 'A unit of length used by several systems equal to 5280 feet with symbol m.'
kids_definition: a unit for measuring distance equal to 1 609 metres or 1 760 yards
simplified: A mile is a unit to measure distance, used in sports and horse racing.

adult_definition: 'Conversation concerning a particular topic.'
kids_definition: a speech or a piece of writing that discusses many different aspects of a subject
simplified: An essay talks about many parts of a topic.

adult_definition: 'A unit of volume equal to 473 millilitres (wet) and 551 millilitres (dry).'
kids_definition: a unit for measuring liquids and some dry goods equal to 0.568 of a litre in the UK and some other countries and 0.473 of a litre in the US. There are 8 pints in a gallon
simplified: We use a pint to measure liquids and some dry things. In the UK, it's a bit more than half a litre. In the US, it's a bit less than half a litre. A gallon has 8 pints.

adult_definition: 'The official currency of Japan.'
kids_definition: the unit of money in Japan
simplified: The money in Japan is called yen.

adult_definition: 'The official currency of South Africa.'
kids_definition: the unit of money in the Republic of South Africa
simplified: The money in South Africa is called the rand, and it's divided into one hundred cents.

adult_definition: 'A flat rigid rectangular structure fixed at right angles to a wall and used to support store or display objects.'
kids_definition: a flat board made of wood metal glass etc. fixed to the wall or forming part of a cupboard bookcase etc. for things to be placed on
simplified: A shelf is a flat board made of wood, metal, or glass that is fixed to the wall or part of a cupboard or bookcase where you can place things.

adult_definition: 'The SI derived unit of pressure or stress with symbol Pa.'
kids_definition: the standard unit for measuring pressure
simplified: The unit we use to measure pressure is called pascal, which means one newton on each square meter.

adult_definition: 'To refuse strongly and solemnly to own or acknowledge.'
kids_definition: to state publicly that you have no knowledge of something or that you are not responsible for something
simplified: Say you don't know or didn't do something.

adult_definition: 'Belonging to them. (genitive of third person plural)'
kids_definition: used instead of his or her to refer to a person whose sex is not mentioned or not known
simplified: We use 'they' instead of 'he' or'she' when we talk about a person and we don't know if they are a boy or a girl.

adult_definition: 'Resulting in success; assuring or promotive of success; accomplishing what was proposed; having the desired effect'
kids_definition: achieving your aims or what was intended
simplified: getting what you wanted to happen from something you did.

adult_definition: 'He when used after a preposition or as the object of a verb. 3rd person singular masculine object pronoun.'
kids_definition: used as the object of a verb after the verb be or after a preposition to refer to a male person or animal that has already been mentioned or is easily identified
simplified: Used to refer to a male person or animal that we already know about.

adult_definition: 'Any of a broad variety of dishes consisting of (usually raw) chopped vegetables most commonly including lettuce.'
kids_definition: a mixture of raw vegetables such as lettuce tomato and cucumber usually served with other food as part of a meal
simplified: We usually eat a mix of vegetables like lettuce, tomato, and cucumber with our meals.

adult_definition: 'A period of time in history seen as a single coherent entity.'
kids_definition: a period of time usually in history that is different from other periods because of particular characteristics or events
simplified: A special time in the past that is unlike other times because of certain things that happened.

adult_definition: 'Meal usually eaten at midday.'
kids_definition: a meal eaten in the middle of the day
simplified: A meal eaten in the day, especially away from home.

adult_definition: 'An item of clothing intended to cover the head made from material hard enough to have a shape independant of the skull and most commonly with a rim.'
kids_definition: a piece of clothing made to fit the head often with a brim (= a flat edge that sticks out) usually worn out of doors
simplified: A hat is a piece of clothing that fits on the head, usually worn outside.

adult_definition: 'A clothing accessory usually made of leather or heavy cloth worn around the waist and used to support trousers or other articles of clothing.'
kids_definition: a long narrow piece of leather cloth etc. that you wear around the middle part of your body
simplified: A belt is a long narrow piece of leather or cloth you wear around your middle to keep your trousers up.

adult_definition: 'An edible plant Brassica oleracea with many varieties.'
kids_definition: a round vegetable with large green purplish-red or white leaves that can be eaten raw or cooked
simplified: We eat a green leafy vegetable, raw or cooked.

adult_definition: The bags and other containers that hold a traveller's belongings.
kids_definition: bags cases etc. that contain somebody's clothes and things when they are travelling
simplified: Some people carry bags with clothes and things when they travel.

adult_definition: The bags and other containers that hold a traveller's belongings.
kids_definition: bags cases etc. that contain somebody's clothes and things when they are travelling
simplified: Some people carry bags with clothes and things when they travel.

adult_definition: 'The part of the body from the neck to the groin excluding the head and limbs.'
kids_definition: the main part of the body not including the head arms or legs
simplified: The body's main part, not including the head, arms, or legs.

adult_definition: 'A musical instrument of the woodwind family.'
kids_definition: a musical instrument of the woodwind group like a thin pipe in shape. The player holds it to the side of his or her face and blows across a hole at one end.
simplified: A woodwind instrument is a long, thin pipe. You hold it to your face and blow across a hole. The air goes through the pipe and out the other end.

adult_definition: 'The speed or pace of a given musical piece.'
kids_definition: the speed or rhythm of a piece of music
simplified: The speed of music can affect the mood it creates.

adult_definition: 'A complex machine or instrument.'
kids_definition: the tools or other pieces of equipment that are needed for a particular activity or task
simplified: The things we need to do a job.

adult_definition: 'The arrangement for a meeting.'
kids_definition: a formal arrangement to meet or visit somebody at a particular time especially for a reason connected with their work
simplified: A special time to meet someone for work is an appointment.

adult_definition: 'An investment firm that purchases a security directly from its issuer for resale or sells it for the issuer.'
kids_definition: a person or organization that underwrites insurance policies especially for ships
simplified: A company that writes insurance policies for boats and goods.

adult_definition: 'A large cup used without a saucer.'
kids_definition: a cup usually made of plastic and often without a handle used for drinking from
simplified: A cup is used for drinking, especially in informal settings.

adult_definition: 'The ability to think about something and use concepts to be able to deal adequately with this.'
kids_definition: an exercise that trains students to understand a language
simplified: An exercise that helps students understand a language model by making sentences that are not the same as a given sentence but still make sense.

adult_definition: 'Free of forgery or counterfeiting.'
kids_definition: known to be real and what somebody claims it is and not a copy
simplified: It's real, not a copy of something, but the thing itself that was copied.

adult_definition: 'Someone who is not known.'
kids_definition: a person that you do not know
simplified: A stranger may come to your house for the first time.

adult_definition: 'The ascent of the sun above the eastern horizon in the morning.'
kids_definition: the time when the sun first appears in the sky in the morning
simplified: When the sun comes up in the morning.

adult_definition: 'The descent of the sun below the western horizon in the evening.'
kids_definition: the colours in the part of the sky where the sun slowly goes down in the evening
simplified: The sky was ablaze with beautiful colours like red, gold, orange, pink, and purple as the sun went down in the evening.

adult_definition: 'The person lawfully in command of a sea-going vessel.'
kids_definition: the person in charge of a ship or commercial aircraft
simplified: The captain of a ship or plane.

adult_definition: 'A quantity of meat fruit or other food baked within or under a crust of prepared pastry.'
kids_definition: a baked dish of fruit or meat and/or vegetables with pastry on the bottom sides and top
simplified: A pie is a baked dish with pastry and fruit, meat, or vegetables.

adult_definition: 'A unit of exchange (such as money) used to facilitate transactions.'
kids_definition: the system of money that a country uses
simplified: The money system of a country is called monetary system.

adult_definition: 'An award offered to recognize the work performed and skills or learning acquired.'
kids_definition: an official document proving that you have completed a course of study or passed an exam; a qualification obtained after a course of study or an exam
simplified: A paper showing you finished school or passed a test; a qualification you get after school or a test.

adult_definition: 'A memento for a specific accomplishment.'
kids_definition: an object such as a silver cup that is given as a prize for winning a competition
simplified: The trophy was a silver cup that the winner of the game got.

adult_definition: 'The daughter of a king queen emperor empress prince or princess.'
kids_definition: a female member of a royal family who is not a queen especially the daughter or granddaughter of the king or queen
simplified: A princess is a woman in a royal family who is not a queen, like a king's daughter or granddaughter.

adult_definition: 'Where light can pass through so one can clearly see through it.'
kids_definition: that you can easily see is false; allowing you to see the truth easily
simplified: It is easy to see that it is false, and then you can easily see the truth.

adult_definition: 'The projection of a mammary gland from which on female mammals milk can be secreted.'
kids_definition: either of the two small round dark parts on a person’s chest. Babies can drink milk from their mother’s breasts through the nipples.
simplified: The two small dark parts on a chest are called nipples. Babies drink milk from mother’s nipples.

adult_definition: 'Either of the two opposable structures forming or near the entrance to the mouth.'
kids_definition: either of the two bones at the bottom of the face that contain the teeth and move when you talk or eat
simplified: The jaw bones move when you talk or eat.

adult_definition: 'The flexible and narrower connection between the forearm and the hand.'
kids_definition: the joint between the hand and the arm
simplified: The wrist is where the hand meets the arm.

adult_definition: 'The area between the pelvis and buttocks and the knee.'
kids_definition: the top part of the leg between the knee and the hip (= where the leg joins the body)
simplified: The top part of the leg between the knee and the hip.

adult_definition: 'The body part that consists of a row of vertebrae that support the head and torso and that forms a canal for nerves.'
kids_definition: the row of small bones that are connected together down the middle of the back
simplified: The little bones in the back are called the vertebrae.

adult_definition: 'A collection of symptoms that characterize a specific disease or condition.'
kids_definition: a set of physical conditions that show you have a particular disease or medical problem
simplified: Some signs in your body that show you have a certain sickness.

adult_definition: 'A stall or light structure for the sale of goods or for display purposes as at a market exhibition or fair.'
kids_definition: a small tent or temporary structure at a market an exhibition or a fairground where you can buy things get information or watch something
simplified: A small tent at a market where you buy things or get information.

adult_definition: 'A stall or light structure for the sale of goods or for display purposes as at a market exhibition or fair.'
kids_definition: a table or small shop with an open front that people sell things from especially at a market
simplified: A small shop with an open front is where people sell things on the street or at a market.

adult_definition: A gouvernment issued proof of identity with which one is allowed to cross a nation's borders.
kids_definition: an official document that identifies you as a citizen of a particular country and that you may have to show when you enter or leave a country
simplified: A special paper that proves you are a citizen of a country and you need to show it when you go into or come out of a country.

adult_definition: 'A type of ditch used in warfare.'
kids_definition: a long deep hole dug in the ground for example for carrying away water
simplified: A deep hole is dug in the ground to carry away water and waste from a building.

adult_definition: 'The intention to do injury to another party.'
kids_definition: with the deliberate intention of committing a crime or harming somebody
simplified: with the intention of doing something bad or harming someone.

adult_definition: 'A person who is owned and forced to work usually without pay by another.'
kids_definition: a person who is owned by another person and is forced to work for and obey them
simplified: A person who must work and obey another person is a slave.

adult_definition: 'The science that deals with concepts such as quantity structure space and change.'
kids_definition: the study of numbers and shapes. Branches of mathematics include arithmetic algebra geometry and trigonometry.
simplified: The study of numbers and shapes is called mathematics. Mathematics has parts like addition subtraction multiplication and division also shapes like points lines and angles.

adult_definition: 'One of the two fields of pre-modern mathematics dealing with spatial relationships.'
kids_definition: the branch of mathematics that deals with the measurements and relationships of lines angles surfaces and solids
simplified: Geometry is the part of math that deals with lines, angles, surfaces, and shapes.

adult_definition: 'A body that has the authority to make and the power to enforce laws within a civil corporate religious academic or other organization or group.'
kids_definition: a particular system or method of controlling a country
simplified: A special way to control a country, group, or activity.

adult_definition: 'A political ideology usually characterised by a very high degree of nationalism economic corporatism a powerful dictatorial leader who portrays the nation state or collective as superior to the individuals or groups composing it.'
kids_definition: an extreme right-wing political system or attitude that is in favour of strong central government aggressively promoting your own country or race above others and that does not allow any opposition
simplified: A system where the government is very strong and wants its country or race to be the best, and does not allow anyone to disagree.

adult_definition: 'A political ideology that seeks to establish a future classless stateless social organization based upon common ownership of the means of production.'
kids_definition: a theory or system of social organization in which all property is owned by the community and each person contributes and receives according to their ability and needs
simplified: A system where everything belongs to everyone, and people help and get what they need.

adult_definition: 'Something that happens or has happened.'
kids_definition: something that happens or exists
simplified: It is something that comes at the same time as something else.

adult_definition: 'Any of various deciduous trees or shrubs in the genus Salix.'
kids_definition: a tree with long thin branches and long thin leaves that often grows near water
simplified: A tree with long branches and long leaves grows near water.

adult_definition: 'An overhead surface that bounds the upper limit of a living space.'
kids_definition: the top inside surface of a room
simplified: The ceiling of the room.

adult_definition: 'Not in accord with the usual regulations.'
kids_definition: relaxed and friendly; not following strict rules of how to behave or do something
simplified: not strict and very friendly.

adult_definition: 'An ideology that holds that a nation is the fundamental unit for human social life and takes precedence over any other social and political principles.'
kids_definition: the desire by a group of people who share the same ethnic group culture language etc. to form an independent country
simplified: A group of people with the same culture wanted to make their own country, which is not a new idea in history.

adult_definition: 'An absolute ruler with unbounded power.'
kids_definition: a political leader who has complete power over a country especially one who has gained it using military force
simplified: A person who rules a country with all the power, often after winning a war.

adult_definition: 'To make something (an object a message) go from one place to another.'
kids_definition: to make something go or be taken to a place especially by post email radio etc.

adult_definition: 'To prepare oneself for a military confrontation.'
kids_definition: to get ready to do something difficult
simplified: To get ready to do something hard.

adult_definition: A woman with one or more siblings who have one or more children; a sister of someone's father or mother.

adult_definition: 'A small fragment of something broken off from the whole.'

kids_definition: the temporary closing of a road or bridge

adult_definition: 'An obstruction in a pipe or tube.'
kids_definition: a situation in which people stop working as part of a protest or strike

adult_definition: 'The point of intersection of the horizontal and vertical axis of a graph.'

adult_definition: 'Being in a state of matrimony.'

adult_definition: 'Postal or other written communications.'

adult_definition: 'The boundary line or the area immediately inside the boundary.'

kids_definition: the number amount or rate of something expressed as if it is part of a total that is 100; a part or share of a whole

kids_definition: a piece of work that somebody has to do especially a hard or unpleasant one

adult_definition: 'The upward-whirling moist air that can form in a thunderstorm.'

adult_definition: 'Glowing white because of intense heat.'
kids_definition: so hot that it looks white

kids_definition: a particular set of beliefs especially about religion or politics

adult_definition: 'A device using gunpowder and other chemicals which when lit emits a combination of coloured flames sparks whistles or bangs for entertainment purposes.'

adult_definition: 'Causing death or having the ability to cause death.'
kids_definition: causing or able to cause death

kids_definition: a sweet sticky yellow-brown substance made by bees that is spread on bread etc. like jam

adult_definition: 'To change a written or spoken text from one language to another.'
kids_definition: to be changed from one language to another

adult_definition: 'A car whose roof can be removed.'
kids_definition: having a roof that you can fold down or take off

adult_definition: 'To provide someone with an incentive to do something.'
kids_definition: to make somebody want to do something especially something that involves hard work and effort

adult_definition: 'A teacher or faculty member at a college or university.'
kids_definition: a teacher at a university or college

kids_definition: a type of heavy oil used as a fuel instead of petrol

simplified: It's a big thin book with a paper cover that comes out every week or month and has articles, pictures, and more, often about one topic; or it's like a collection of articles online that comes out regularly.

kids_definition: a person who travels to a holy place for religious reasons

adult_definition: 'A gemstone-quality transparent variety of beryl.'

kids_definition: a person whose job is to cut men’s hair and sometimes to shave them

adult_definition: 'A type of circular intersection in which traffic must travel in one direction around a central island.'

adult_definition: 'A string or strip of pasta especially as used in Chinese and Italian cookery.'

adult_definition: 'Regarding abstractions namely concepts ideas thoughts etc.'
kids_definition: a person who is untouchable is in a position where they are unlikely to be punished or criticized
simplified: Someone who is untouchable is safe from punishment or criticism.

adult_definition: Withdrawal from one's occupation or active working life: having concluded one's working or professional career.
kids_definition: the act of stopping a particular type of work especially in sport politics etc.; the period of your life after a career in sport politics etc.
simplified: The time after you stop playing a sport or doing a job in politics.

adult_definition: 'A short piece of text often numbered placed at the bottom of a printed page that adds a comment citation reference etc to a designated part of the main text.'
kids_definition: an extra piece of information that is given at the bottom of a page below the main text
simplified: Some words are written at the bottom of a page to help you understand better.

adult_definition: 'The action of coming to a foreign country or region to which one is not native in order to settle there.'
kids_definition: the process of coming to live permanently in a different country from the one you were born in; the number of people who do this
simplified: When people move to a new country to live, it is called settling. More people are doing this every year.

adult_definition: 'The act or an instance of considering.'
kids_definition: the act of thinking carefully about something
simplified: When you think carefully about something, you can make a good decision.

adult_definition: 'An enclosed space or piece of furniture where clothes are kept.'
kids_definition: a small room or a space in a wall with a door that reaches the floor used for storing things
simplified: A cupboard is a small room or space in a wall with a door that goes down to the floor to store things.

adult_definition: 'Given to expressing yourself freely or insistently.'
kids_definition: telling people your opinions or protesting about something loudly and with confidence
simplified: Telling people what you think or saying loudly what you don't like.

adult_definition: 'An individual or organization that creates goods or services.'
kids_definition: a person a company or a country that grows or makes food goods or materials
simplified: A farmer, a company or a country makes food that other people use.

adult_definition: 'Lacking in taste or vigor.'
kids_definition: not having a strong or interesting taste
simplified: The food was disappointing because it didn't have a strong or interesting taste.

adult_definition: 'The feel of a surface or a fabric.'
kids_definition: the way a surface substance or piece of cloth feels when you touch it for example how rough smooth hard or soft it is
simplified: How things feel when we touch them.

adult_definition: 'Of an species of organisms that no longer exist alive.'
kids_definition: no longer in existence in society
simplified: It is no longer there in our world.

adult_definition: 'A material or object that produces a magnetic field.'
kids_definition: a piece of iron that attracts objects made of iron towards it either naturally or because of an electric current that is passed through it
simplified: A magnet is a piece of iron that pulls other iron things towards it.

adult_definition: 'Produced by synthesis instead of being isolated from a natural source.'
kids_definition: artificial; made by combining chemical substances rather than being produced naturally by plants or animals
simplified: The medicine is made from chemicals rather than from plants or animals.

adult_definition: 'To take back something one has said.'
kids_definition: to say that something you have said earlier is not true or correct or that you did not mean it
simplified: To take back something you said earlier that was not true or not meant that way.

adult_definition: 'Subjectively experienced sensations in the absence of an appropriate stimulus but which are regarded by the individual as real.'
kids_definition: the fact of seeming to see or hear somebody/something that is not really there especially because of illness or drugs
simplified: Sometimes we think we see or hear things that are not really there, especially when we are sick or have taken some medicine.

adult_definition: 'The consciousness or awareness of dishonor disgrace or condemnation.'
kids_definition: the ability to feel shame at something you have done
simplified: Feeling sorry for doing something wrong is a sign of being strong, not weak.

adult_definition: 'Any problem where the answer is very complex possibly unsolvable without deep investigation.'
kids_definition: a confusing problem or question that is very difficult to solve
simplified: A hard puzzle or question that is very tricky to solve or answer.

adult_definition: 'An opening in the lightpath of a lens or objective that can regulate the amount of light that passes.'
kids_definition: a thin disc used to turn electronic signals into sound and sound into electronic signals in phones loudspeakers etc.
simplified: A small round thing helps make sounds come out and takes sounds in, like in phones and speakers.

adult_definition: 'A metal-tipped spear thrown for distance in an athletic field event'
kids_definition: a light spear (= a long stick with a pointed end) that is thrown in a sporting event
simplified: A spear was coming towards him from the side of the field.

adult_definition: 'An implement with a handle connected to a round frame strung with wire sinew or plastic cords and used to hit a ball such as in tennis or a birdie in badminton.'
kids_definition: a piece of sports equipment used for hitting the ball etc. in the games of tennis squash or badminton. It has an oval frame with strings stretched across and down it.
simplified: A racket is used for hitting a ball in games like tennis, squash, or badminton. It has an oval frame with strings.

adult_definition: 'Accidental overheating of the core of a nuclear reactor resulting in the core melting and radiation escaping.'
kids_definition: a serious accident in which the central part of a nuclear reactor melts causing harmful radiation to escape
simplified: A very bad accident happened at a nuclear reactor, and bad things came out into the air.

adult_definition: 'A formal lengthy exposition of some subject.'
kids_definition: a long and serious treatment or discussion of a subject in speech or writing
simplified: A long and important talk or writing about a subject.

adult_definition: 'The presence of a wide range of variation in the qualities or attributes that are being observed.'
kids_definition: the quality or fact of including a range of many people or things
simplified: Diversity means having many kinds of people, things, or ideas together.

adult_definition: 'ordered; conform a fixed procedure.'
kids_definition: following a pattern especially with the same time or space in between each thing and the next
simplified: We put things in a pattern with the same time or space between each thing and the next.

adult_definition: 'To have enough courage (to do something).'
kids_definition: to be brave enough to do something
simplified: To be brave means to take a risk and try, even if you might fail.

adult_definition: 'Having power over all others.'
kids_definition: very great or the greatest in degree
simplified: very, very good or the best.

adult_definition: 'Pliers made of steel for removing nails from wood.'
kids_definition: a tool made of two crossed pieces of metal used for holding things and pulling things for example nails out of wood
simplified: A tool with two crossed metal pieces is used to hold and pull things like nails out of wood.

adult_definition: 'Of or pertaining to the father his genes his relatives or his side of a family.'
kids_definition: related through the father’s side of the family
simplified: The girl's family was related to the father's family, but not to the mother's family, who had lived there for a long time.

adult_definition: 'Of or pertaining to the mother her genes her relatives or her side of a family.'
kids_definition: related through the mother’s side of the family
simplified: The two are related on their mothers' side.

adult_definition: 'A bitter brownish-yellow or greenish-yellow secretion produced by the liver stored in the gallbladder and discharged into the duodenum where it aids the process of digestion.'
kids_definition: the green-brown liquid with a bitter unpleasant taste that is produced by the liver to help the body to deal with the fats we eat and that can come into your mouth when you vomit with an empty stomach
simplified: The bitter liquid made by the liver to help with fats we eat is bile.

adult_definition: 'Someone who risks loss or injury in the hope of gain or excitement'
kids_definition: a person who is willing to risk losing something in the hope of being successful
simplified: Someone who takes a chance to win something but might lose.

adult_definition: 'The variation typically in time of some measure about a central value often a point of equilibrium or between two or more different states.'
kids_definition: a single movement from one position to another of something that is oscillating
simplified: A movement from one place to another of something that goes back and forth.

adult_definition: 'An officer of the court who is employed to execute writs and processes and make arrests.'
kids_definition: an official who keeps order in court takes people to their seats watches prisoners etc.
simplified: Official helps people to their seats, watches prisoners.

adult_definition: 'Any vehicle designed to be towed with the exception of a caravan.'
kids_definition: a truck or a container with wheels that is pulled by another vehicle
simplified: A thing on wheels that another vehicle pulls.

adult_definition: 'Communicating in a sign language.'
kids_definition: the act of using sign language
simplified: Signing is when you use your hands to talk.

adult_definition: 'Without break cessation or interruption.'
kids_definition: happening or existing for a period of time without being interrupted
simplified: It has been going on for a long time.

adult_definition: 'Without break cessation or interruption.'
kids_definition: very large in size or amount and seeming to have no end
simplified: extremely big or a lot and never-ending.

adult_definition: 'A temporary state of custody or confinement especially of a prisoner awaiting trial.'
kids_definition: the state of being kept in a place especially a prison and prevented from leaving
simplified: The state of being locked up and not allowed to leave.

adult_definition: 'An official list of candidates during an election.'
kids_definition: a list of the candidates in an election
simplified: The names of the people running in the election.

adult_definition: 'Not connected with spiritual or religious matters.'
kids_definition: not connected with spiritual or religious matters
simplified: It is not about spiritual or religious things.

adult_definition: 'Surgical excision or amputation of a body part or tissue.'
kids_definition: the use of surgery to remove body tissue
simplified: Doctors often take samples of body tissue to study in medical research.

adult_definition: 'A tree or shrub in any species of the genus Magnolia many with large flowers and simple leaves.'
kids_definition: a tree with large white pink or purple flowers that smell sweet
simplified: A sweet-smelling tree with big, colorful flowers attracts many bees.

adult_definition: 'A method of putting liquid into the body with a hollow needle and a syringe which is pierced through the skin long enough for the material to be forced into the body.'
kids_definition: an act of forcing a liquid or other substance into something
simplified: When you push a liquid or something else through a small hole, it is called an act of forcing.

adult_definition: 'An occupation requiring specialized knowledge.'
kids_definition: a type of job that needs special training or skill especially one that needs a high level of education
simplified: A job that needs special training, skill, and a lot of education and experience.

adult_definition: 'A condition that results from excessive loss of water from a living organism.'
kids_definition: the condition of having lost too much water from your body
simplified: When you lose too much water from your body, you feel weak and your mouth gets dry.

adult_definition: 'A simplified language that develops as a means of communication between two or more groups who do not share a common language in situations such as trade.'
kids_definition: a simple form of a language especially English Portuguese or Dutch with a limited number of words that are used together with words from a local language. It is used when people who do not speak the same language need to talk to each other.
simplified: A simple way of talking with few words from two languages when people who do not speak the same language need to talk.

adult_definition: 'To pardon or remit (a sin).'
kids_definition: to state formally that somebody is not guilty or responsible for something
simplified: A judge said the man did no wrong.

adult_definition: 'Able to be reached or approached easily.'
kids_definition: that can be reached entered used etc. by somebody who has problems walking
simplified: If the place is not accessible for people who have trouble walking or use a wheelchair, they won't be able to get in and that's a big problem.

adult_definition: The idea of an advance that occurs within the limits of mankind's collective morality and knowledge of its respective environment.
kids_definition: the process of improving or developing or of getting nearer to achieving or completing something
simplified: It is a process of making slow and steady progress towards achieving something.

adult_definition: 'To fail to attend to.'
kids_definition: to fail to take care of somebody/something
simplified: Not taking care of someone/something that needs it.

adult_definition: 'A measure for the speed (amount of data) that can be sent through an Internet connection.'
kids_definition: a measurement of the amount of information that a particular computer network or internet connection can send in a particular time. It is often measured in bits per second.
simplified: A speed test sees how much information a computer network or internet can send at once.

adult_definition: 'A method of sending audio and video files over the Internet in such a way that the user can view the file while it is being transferred.'
kids_definition: a method of sending or receiving data especially video or sound over a computer network
simplified: A way to send or get video or sound on a computer network like the internet.

adult_definition: 'To bring to a succesful end; to gain with effort.'
kids_definition: to succeed in reaching a particular goal status or standard especially by making an effort for a long time
simplified: To reach a high goal, you must work hard for a long time.

adult_definition: 'Having to do with hearing or with sound.'
kids_definition: related to sound or to the sense of hearing
simplified: This is about sound and how we hear.

adult_definition: 'Having the position next to a given place location or object'
kids_definition: unable to control yourself because of the strength of emotion you are feeling
simplified: You are acting badly because you can't control your strong feelings and it may hurt others.

adult_definition: 'Giving cause for legal action.'
kids_definition: giving somebody a legally acceptable reason to bring a case to court
simplified: It is an order from a judge to do something.

adult_definition: 'Characterized by energetic work participation etc.'
kids_definition: in a way that involves making a determined effort and not leaving something to happen by itself
simplified: Doing something on purpose is not often seen in fairy tales, but it is common in real-life stories.

adult_definition: 'An actual condition or circumstance.'
kids_definition: the state of something existing in reality
simplified: The state of something real.

adult_definition: 'Something that beautifies or adorns.'
kids_definition: something that you wear to make yourself look more attractive; something used to decorate a place or an object
simplified: Something to make yourself or things look nicer.

adult_definition: 'A forward step; an improvement.'
kids_definition: the process of helping something/somebody to make progress or succeed; the progress that is made
simplified: Helping someone to do better and getting good results.

adult_definition: 'A unit that expresses a mass or number.'
kids_definition: the measurement of something by saying how much of it there is
simplified: We call it quantity when we say how much of something is there using a standard unit.

adult_definition: 'Closed group of people that belong to the same category.'
kids_definition: one of the groups of an army with a special responsibility
simplified: The vanguard is a special group that goes ahead of the main army and prepares the way.

adult_definition: 'Containing one error or several errors.'
kids_definition: based on a wrong opinion or bad judgement
simplified: because of a wrong idea

adult_definition: 'Containing one error or several errors.'
kids_definition: wrong or containing mistakes often resulting in bad decisions
simplified: Sometimes we make mistakes which lead to bad choices.

adult_definition: 'Containing one error or several errors.'
kids_definition: having a fault or faults; not perfect or complete
simplified: having something wrong with it.

adult_definition: 'An act that violates the rules of a sport.'
kids_definition: done against the rules of a sport
simplified: broke the rules.

adult_definition: 'Unpleasant offensive or causing dislike.'
kids_definition: causing a feeling of strong dislike; very unpleasant
simplified: The man was very unpleasant and caused a strong dislike.

adult_definition: 'Sentenced to eternal punishment in hell.'
kids_definition: having a curse on it; suffering from a curse
simplified: had a curse on it.

adult_definition: 'A substance to repel insects.'
kids_definition: not letting a particular substance especially water pass through it
simplified: Not letting water go through it.

adult_definition: 'An exciting or very unusual experience.'
kids_definition: an unusual exciting or dangerous experience journey or series of events
simplified: A strange and exciting adventure.

adult_definition: 'A person who has enjoys or seeks adventures.'
kids_definition: a person who enjoys exciting new experiences especially going to unusual places
simplified: An adventurer is a person who likes to try new things, like going to strange places and eating new foods and drinks.

adult_definition: 'Liking or eager for adventure.'
kids_definition: full of new exciting or dangerous experiences
simplified: Full of exciting experiences.

adult_definition: 'The profession or work of an advocate.'
kids_definition: public support that somebody gives to an idea a course of action or a belief
simplified: People support an idea or a person.

adult_definition: 'The spouse usually of royalty or of a deity.'
kids_definition: the husband or wife of a king queen ruler etc.
simplified: The husband or wife of a king or queen is called a king or queen.

adult_definition: 'A social or business relationship.'
kids_definition: a person’s connection with a political party religion etc.
simplified: A person's friends and things they believe in can affect their thoughts about some things.

adult_definition: 'An inherent similarity between persons or things.'
kids_definition: a close relationship between two people or things that have similar qualities structures or features
simplified: A connection between two things that are alike.

adult_definition: 'The assertion that something exists or is true.'
kids_definition: a definite or public statement that something is true or that you support something strongly
simplified: Said that something was true or they liked it very much.

adult_definition: 'Care and treatment of a convalescent patient.'
kids_definition: care or treatment given to a person who has just left hospital prison etc.
simplified: Help given to someone who has just been freed.

adult_definition: 'Any offensive action attack or procedure.'
kids_definition: a violent attack or threats by one person against another person or by one country against another country
simplified: When someone or a country hurts or threatens someone else, it shows they are weak and scared, not strong and brave.

adult_definition: 'Unhappy or hurt because of unjust treatment.'
kids_definition: feeling that you have been treated unfairly
simplified: Feeling that you have been treated unfairly is very difficult and painful.

adult_definition: 'A sudden recurrence of a disease.'
kids_definition: a sudden short attack of pain causing physical shaking that cannot be controlled
simplified: A sudden, sharp pain that makes you shake all over.

adult_definition: 'The power of moving quickly and easily.'
kids_definition: the ability to move quickly and easily
simplified: Being able to move fast and easily was a big help in the forest.

adult_definition: 'Exposure to air for freshening or drying.'
kids_definition: the act of allowing warm air to make clothes beds etc. fresh and dry
simplified: Ironing makes clothes fresh and dry in a short time.

adult_definition: 'Characterized by truth or logic.'
kids_definition: based on reason rather than emotions
simplified: We can make better choices when we think with our heads, not our feelings.

adult_definition: 'Poorly ventilated without fresh air.'
kids_definition: warm in an unpleasant way and without enough fresh air
simplified: The room was warm and stuffy.

adult_definition: 'An airtight chamber usually located between two regions of unequal pressure in which air pressure can be regulated.'
kids_definition: a small room with a tightly closed door at each end which you go through to reach another area at a different air pressure for example on a spacecraft or submarine
simplified: You go through a small room with closed doors at each end to reach another area with different air pressure, like on a spacecraft or submarine.

adult_definition: 'A regular course followed by aircraft.'
kids_definition: a route regularly used by planes
simplified: A way that planes and boats often use would be shut for a few days, making many travelers unhappy.

adult_definition: 'The fact or a statement that a person accused of a crime was somewhere else when it was committed.'
kids_definition: evidence that proves that a person was in another place at the time of a crime and so could not have committed it
simplified: Proof that someone was somewhere else when a crime happened, so they couldn't have done it.

adult_definition: 'The splitting of a heavy nucleus into two roughly equal parts (which are nuclei of lower-mass elements) accompanied by the release of a relatively large amount of energy in the form of kinetic energy of the two parts and in the form of emission of neutrons and gamma rays .'
kids_definition: the act or process of splitting the nucleus (= central part) of an atom when a large amount of energy is released
simplified: When an atom splits, a lot of energy is released.

adult_definition: 'The idea that the like results of the good and evil a person does will return either in this life or in a later one.'
kids_definition: the sum of somebody’s good and bad actions in one of their lives believed to decide what will happen to them in the next life
simplified: What someone does good or bad in their life decides what happens to them next.

adult_definition: 'Someone who studies or practices philosophy'
kids_definition: a person who studies or writes about philosophy
simplified: A philosopher is someone who studies or writes about philosophy.

adult_definition: 'The study of religion and religious belief or a particular system or school of religious beliefs and teachings.'
kids_definition: the study of religion and beliefs
simplified: The group looked at how different cultures believed and worshipped.

adult_definition: 'The quality dignity office or territorial competence of any Emir.'
kids_definition: the period of time that an emir rules
simplified: When a king rules a country, we call the time he rules the king's reign.

adult_definition: 'A political entity that formally agrees by treaty to enter into an unequal relationship with another stronger state called the protector which engages to protect it against third parties in exchange for which the protectorate usually accepts specified obligations which may vary greatly depending on the real nature of their relationship. '
kids_definition: the state or period of being controlled and protected by another country
simplified: When one country is ruled or protected by another country, government, or power.

adult_definition: 'A hard rounded object produced within the soft tissue (specifically the mantle) of a living shelled mollusk.'
kids_definition: a small hard shiny white ball that forms inside the shell of an oyster and is of great value as a jewel
simplified: A small, shiny, white ball that grows inside an oyster shell is very valuable as a jewel.

adult_definition: 'Joined by political agreement or treaty.'
kids_definition: (of two or more things) similar or existing together; connected with something
simplified: Are similar, together, connected, or done at the same time.

adult_definition: 'An annual publication containing a calendar for the coming year the times of such events and phenomena as anniversaries sunrises and sunsets phases of the moon tides etc. and other statistical information and related topics.'
kids_definition: a book or digital resource that gives information about the sun moon times of the tides (= the rise and fall of the sea level) etc. for each day of the year
simplified: A book or computer thing that tells us when the sun and moon come up and go down and when the sea gets bigger and smaller each day.

adult_definition: 'Condition that occurs when every individual within a population has the same allele at a particular locus.'
kids_definition: a very strong interest in somebody/something that is unusual or not reasonable
simplified: People are very interested in strange things.

adult_definition: 'Ready or willing to answer act agree or yield.'
kids_definition: easy to control; willing to be influenced by somebody/something
simplified: easy to persuade.

adult_definition: 'The standard SI unit of electrical current with symbol A.'
kids_definition: the unit for measuring electric current
simplified: The unit for measuring electric current is called the ampere.

adult_definition: 'Living or able to live both on land and in water.'
kids_definition: able to live both on land and in water
simplified: Can live on land and in water.

adult_definition: 'An oval or circular building with rows of seats surrounding a central space used as a theatre or arena.'
kids_definition: a room hall or theatre with rows of seats that rise in steps
simplified: A room with steps of seats like a staircase.

adult_definition: 'To occupy in an agreeable entertaining or pleasant fashion.'
kids_definition: to make somebody laugh or smile
simplified: To make someone happy.

adult_definition: 'A domesticated subspecies or infrasubspecies of an animal.'
kids_definition: knowing somebody/something very well may cause you to lose respect for them/it
simplified: If you know someone very well, you may not respect them as much.

adult_definition: 'A place which is safe or used for anchoring boats.'
kids_definition: a place where ships or boats can anchor
simplified: A place where boats can stop safely.

adult_definition: 'Yearly historical accounts of events.'
kids_definition: an official record of events or activities year by year; historical records
simplified: A list of what happened each year.

adult_definition: 'A person who introduces programmes or reads the news on radio or television.'
kids_definition: a person who introduces or gives information about programmes on the radio or television
simplified: Someone who talks about TV or radio shows.

adult_definition: 'To make someone rather angry or impatient; to cause annoyance.'
kids_definition: to make somebody uncomfortable or unable to relax
simplified: to make someone feel uneasy or worried about something.

adult_definition: 'The annual payment of an allowance or income.'
kids_definition: a type of insurance that pays a fixed amount of money to somebody each year
simplified: A type of insurance that pays a fixed amount of money each year for the rest of life in exchange for a payment now.

adult_definition: 'The farthest points at which the sun can be directly overhead; the boundaries of the torrid zone or tropics.'
kids_definition: the area between the two tropics which is the hottest part of the world
simplified: The hottest part of the world is called the equatorial region.

adult_definition: 'A kind of heavy jacket.'
kids_definition: a short coat with a hood that is worn as protection against rain wind and cold
simplified: A coat with a hood helps keep you warm and dry in rain, wind, or cold weather.

adult_definition: 'The process whereby a population of animals or plants becomes accustomed to human provision and control.'
kids_definition: the process of making a plant or crop suitable to grow for human use
simplified: Making a plant or crop grow to be useful for humans.

adult_definition: 'A process whereby some proportion of the output signal of a system is passed (fed back) to the input. This is often used to control the dynamic behavior of the system.'
kids_definition: the unpleasant noise produced by electrical equipment such as an amplifier when some of the power returns to the system
simplified: The bad sound from things like amplifiers happens when some power goes back into the system through the ground instead of being used.

adult_definition: 'With an uncontrolled need to do things.'
kids_definition: not being able to control their behaviour
simplified: They were ordered to work in the garden at the back of the house because they could not control themselves.

adult_definition: 'Various religious writings of uncertain origin regarded by some as inspired but rejected by most authorities.'
kids_definition: Christian religious texts that are related to the Bible but not officially considered to be part of it
simplified: Christian texts that are related to the Bible but not officially part of it are called Apocrypha.

adult_definition: A mark (') which is used to show that a letter or letters has/have been omitted from a word.
kids_definition: the mark ( ’ ) used to show that one or more letters or numbers have been left out as in she’s for she is and ’63 for 1963
simplified: The mark ( ’ ) is used to show that some letters or numbers are left out, like she’s for she is and ’63 for 1963.

adult_definition: 'The elevation or exaltation of a person to the rank of a god.'
kids_definition: a formal statement that a person has become a god
simplified: The king said a person became a god.

adult_definition: 'To bring to a state of peace quiet ease calm or contentment.'
kids_definition: to make somebody calmer or less angry by giving them what they want
simplified: To make someone feel better by giving them what they want.

adult_definition: 'A subordinate part attached to something.'
kids_definition: a thing that is added or attached to something larger or more important
simplified: A part that is added to something bigger.

adult_definition: 'A small portion of a food or drink served before or at the beginning of a meal to stimulate the desire to eat.'
kids_definition: a small amount of food or a drink that you have before a meal
simplified: A little food or drink before a meal to make you hungry.

adult_definition: 'One who estimates officially the worth or value or quality of things.'
kids_definition: a person whose job is to examine a building an object etc. and say how much it is worth
simplified: A person who checks the value of things like buildings and objects is called an appraiser.

adult_definition: 'A piece of cloth plastic worn over the front of the clothes for protection against dirt.'
kids_definition: a piece of clothing worn over the front of the body from the chest or the waist down and tied around the waist. Aprons are worn over other clothes to keep them clean for example when cooking.
simplified: An apron is a piece of clothing that you wear over your clothes to keep them clean.

adult_definition: 'A nobleman of hereditary rank in various European monarchies and some of their colonies.'
kids_definition: (in some European countries but not the UK) a nobleman of high rank between a count and a duke
simplified: A marquess is a nobleman of high rank between a count and a duke.

adult_definition: 'A member of the lowest grade of nobility.'
kids_definition: a nobleman of the lowest rank. In the UK barons use the title Lord; in other countries they use the title Baron.
simplified: A noble person with a low rank is called Lord in the UK, but Baron in other countries.

adult_definition: 'Barren or unproductive because of lack of moisture.'
kids_definition: having little or no rain; very dry
simplified: very dry because it has little rain.

adult_definition: 'The place where weapons are made or kept.'
kids_definition: a place where weapons and armour are kept
simplified: A place where swords and shields are kept.

adult_definition: 'Passerine bird of the family Alaudidae.'
kids_definition: a small brown bird with a pleasant song
simplified: A little brown bird sat on a branch of a tall tree and sang a nice song.

adult_definition: 'Marked by skill in achieving a desidered goal usually in a bad sense.'
kids_definition: clever at getting what you want sometimes by not telling the truth
simplified: You are good at getting what you want, but sometimes you don't tell the truth.

adult_definition: A tall thistlelike composite plant ''Cynara scolymus'' native to the Mediterranean region of which the numerous scalelike bracts and receptacle of the immature flower head are eaten as a vegetable.
kids_definition: a round vegetable with a lot of thick green leaves. The bottom part of the leaves and the inside of the artichoke can be eaten when cooked.
simplified: An artichoke has green leaves. You can eat the leaves and the inside when cooked.

adult_definition: 'Any of several venomous snakes of Africa Asia and Europe.'
kids_definition: a general name for various types of small poisonous snake found in North Africa
simplified: A general name for various small poisonous snakes in North Africa and Asia.

adult_definition: 'A curved pointed appendage found at the end of a toe or finger or in arthropods of the tarsus.'
kids_definition: a long sharp curved part of the body of some types of shellfish used for catching and holding things
simplified: A claw is a curved part of some shellfish used for catching things.

adult_definition: 'A positive statement or declaration often without support or reason.'
