adult_definition: 'To twist or roll into coils spirals or ringlets.'
kids_definition: to form or make something form into a curl or curls
simplified: Make something curl up.

adult_definition: 'To derive or receive pleasure from; get enjoyment from; take pleasure in.'
kids_definition: to enjoy a feeling or an experience completely
simplified: To fully enjoy something.

adult_definition: 'The state of being alone in solitary isolation.'
kids_definition: the fact of a period of time being sad and spent alone
simplified: Feeling sad and lonely made me feel sad and lonely.

adult_definition: 'The expressive and pleasurable feeling from an emotional attraction towards another person associated with romantic love.'
kids_definition: love or the feeling of being in love
simplified: Love is hard to explain or show, but it is special and makes us happy.

adult_definition: 'To grip or seize as in a wrestling match.'
kids_definition: to take a strong hold of somebody/something and struggle with them
simplified: To hold someone/something tightly and fight to control them/it.

adult_definition: 'Of or pertaining to a number system have 2 as its base.'
kids_definition: using only 0 and 1 as a system of numbers
simplified: We can easily do big calculations using just 0 and 1.

adult_definition: To imagine conceive or see in one's mind.
kids_definition: to imagine what a situation will be like in the future especially a situation you intend to work towards
simplified: Imagine how things will be in the future, especially something you want to happen and make real.

adult_definition: 'To make something blessed; to confer blessing upon.'
kids_definition: to call God holy; to praise God
simplified: We should respect God, thank Him, keep the holy day, honor our parents, not kill, not cheat, not steal, not lie, and not want things that belong to others.

adult_definition: 'To cause to be quiet or not talk.'
kids_definition: to be quiet; to stop talking or crying
simplified: Be quiet. Stop talking or crying.

adult_definition: 'To join together by heating.'
kids_definition: to join pieces of metal together by heating their edges and pressing them together
simplified: to join metal pieces together by heating and pressing their edges.

adult_definition: 'To fly in or as if in a glider plane.'
kids_definition: to fly using air currents without the birds moving their wings or the aircraft using the engine
simplified: The king told the little prince that the birds fly high in the air without moving their wings.

adult_definition: 'To move in an abrupt or headlong manner.'
kids_definition: to throw or push somebody/something with force especially because you are angry or in a careless way
simplified: You push or throw something hard when you are angry or careless.

adult_definition: 'To move forward by leaps and bounds.'
kids_definition: to increase suddenly and by a large amount
simplified: Grow much bigger all of a sudden.

adult_definition: 'To throw catch and keep in the air several things simultaneously.'
kids_definition: to throw a set of three or more objects such as balls into the air and catch and throw them again quickly one at a time so as to keep at least one in the air at all times
simplified: To throw and catch balls in the air, one at a time, so at least one stays up in the air.

adult_definition: 'To breathe noisily as when one is exhausted.'
kids_definition: to breathe quickly with short breaths usually with your mouth open because you have been doing some physical exercise or because it is very hot
simplified: You breathe quickly with short breaths when you exercise or it is hot outside.

adult_definition: 'To use again after processing by converting waste into reusable material.'
kids_definition: to treat things that have already been used so that they can be used again
simplified: to make old things useful again.

adult_definition: 'To separate the grain from the straw or husks by beating.'
kids_definition: to hit a person or an animal many times with a stick etc. as a punishment
simplified: Hit someone or an animal with a stick many times as punishment.

adult_definition: 'To injure by stomping or as if by stomping.'
kids_definition: to step heavily on somebody/something so that you damage or harm them/it with your feet
simplified: Step on someone/something heavily to hurt them/it.

adult_definition: 'To walk (through relatively shallow water).'
kids_definition: to walk or stand with no shoes or socks in shallow water in the sea a lake etc.
simplified: To walk or stand in water with no shoes or socks.

adult_definition: 'A corporal punishment inflicted with repeated blows.'
kids_definition: an act of hitting somebody hard and repeatedly as a punishment or in a fight
simplified: He hit him hard many times.

adult_definition: 'To take the load off (a container or vehicle).'
kids_definition: to remove things from a vehicle or ship after it has taken them somewhere
simplified: "Unload" means to take things out of a car, bus, or boat after it has taken them somewhere.

adult_definition: 'To lie in wait lie in ambush behave in a sneaky and secretive manner.'
kids_definition: to wait somewhere secretly especially because you are going to do something bad or illegal
simplified: To wait somewhere secretly because you are going to do something wrong or are afraid of being caught.

adult_definition: 'To direct the course (e.g. of a vehicle); determine the direction of travelling.'
kids_definition: to control the direction in which a boat car etc. moves
simplified: To control where a boat car goes when it is not on the track.

adult_definition: 'A unit of information equal to 1000 megabytes or 10^9 (1000000000) bytes.'
kids_definition: a unit of computer memory or data equal to 109 or 1 0003 (= 1 000 000 000) bytes
simplified: It's a big unit of computer memory or data.

adult_definition: 'A unit of information equal to 1000 gigabytes or 10^12 (1000000000000) bytes.'
kids_definition: a unit of computer memory or data equal to one million million or 1012 (= 1 000 000 000 000) bytes
simplified: A big unit of computer memory or data is one million million bytes.

adult_definition: 'Characteristic of or affected by neurosis.'
kids_definition: caused by or having neurosis (= a mental illness in which a person has strong feelings of fear and worry)
simplified: It is caused by fear and worry or a personality problem.

adult_definition: 'Of or relating to ontology.'
kids_definition: connected with the branch of philosophy that deals with the nature of existence
simplified: It is about the part of philosophy that talks about what exists, who we are, and what is real.

adult_definition: 'Having hardness and rigidity but little tensile strength.'
kids_definition: a brittle mood or state of mind is one that appears to be happy or strong but is actually nervous and easily damaged
simplified: When someone seems happy and strong, but is actually nervous and easily hurt, they are in a brittle mood.

adult_definition: 'Farmer who specializes in the production of milk; the owner of a diary.'
kids_definition: a man who works in a dairy
simplified: A man works on a farm making milk and cheese.

adult_definition: 'To gather the ripened crop.'
kids_definition: to cut and collect a crop especially wheat from a field
simplified: Harvest wheat from a field.

adult_definition: 'Muscular capacity to modify the speed of an external physical object to deform it or to oppose another force.'
kids_definition: used to say that something seems the best thing to do in the situation that you are in although you may not really want to do it
simplified: It would be the best thing to do, even if you don't want to.

adult_definition: 'The act of firing a projectile.'
kids_definition: the act of firing a gun; the sound this makes
simplified: Firing a gun makes a loud sound, a bright flash, a bad smell, and a strong kickback. It shoots a fast bullet that can cause a lot of damage.

adult_definition: 'The bottom or lowest part.'
kids_definition: the reason why people take a particular action
simplified: The reason people do something is often hidden in their minds, and they or others may not know it.

adult_definition: 'Gipsy is a common word used to indicate Romani people Tinkers and Travellers.'
kids_definition: a member of an ethnic group (= a people who share a cultural tradition) originally from Asia who traditionally travel around and live in caravans. Many people prefer to use the name Roma or Romani.
simplified: A Romani is a person from Asia who travels around and lives in a caravan.

adult_definition: 'Gipsy is a common word used to indicate Romani people Tinkers and Travellers.'
kids_definition: a member of an ethnic group (= a group of people with a shared cultural background language etc.) originally from Asia who traditionally travel around and live in caravans. Many people prefer to use the name Roma or Romani.
simplified: A person from Asia who travels around and lives in a caravan with others like them. They are also called Roma or Romani.

adult_definition: 'Person who habitually eats and drinks excessively.'
kids_definition: a person who eats too much
simplified: A person who eats much food.

adult_definition: A hump may refer to a camel's hump containing its fat reservoir or alternatively to the curve on an upper spine that causes a hunchback.
kids_definition: a round part that sticks out on the back of a person caused by an unusual curve in the spine (= the row of bones in the middle of the back)
simplified: A person with a bent spine has a round part sticking out of their back.

adult_definition: 'Tender and amiable; of a considerate or kindly disposition.'
kids_definition: quiet gentle and always ready to do what other people want without expressing your own opinion
simplified: Always doing what others want without saying what you think.

adult_definition: 'A large number of something.'
kids_definition: an extremely large number of things or people
simplified: A lot of things or people.

adult_definition: The class of literature comprising poems; a poet's literary production; composition in verse or language exhibiting conscious attention to patterns.
kids_definition: poems in general; poems as a genre of literature
simplified: Poetry is a type of writing.

adult_definition: 'Of pertaining to or containing spice; or spicy flavour: Provoking a burning sensation due to the presence of chillies or similar hot spices.'
kids_definition: having a strong taste because spices have been added to it
simplified: It tastes strong because spices have been added to it.

adult_definition: 'Any of various large coniferous evergreen trees from the genus Picea found in northern temperate and boreal regions.'
kids_definition: an evergreen forest tree with leaves like needles
simplified: A tree with needle leaves.

adult_definition: 'The overside or up-side of a flat object such as a table or of a liquid; the outside hull of a tangible object.'
kids_definition: the outer appearance of a person thing or situation; the qualities that you see or notice that are not hidden
simplified: The way someone or something looks on the outside.

adult_definition: 'Referring to something or someone that has received an infection.'
kids_definition: affected by harmful bacteria a virus etc.
simplified: Some germs, like bad bacteria or a virus, don't make people sick on their own. Instead, they trigger a chain of events that make someone ill. That's why some people get sick and others don't.

adult_definition: 'To weaken or make thinner by adding a foreign substance or a solvent (e.g. water) to a solution.'
kids_definition: to make a liquid weaker by adding water or another liquid to it
simplified: When you add water to something, it makes it weaker.

adult_definition: 'To (accidentally) dislodge a skeletal bone from its joint.'
kids_definition: to put a bone out of its normal position in a joint
simplified: When a bone gets out of place in a joint, like in a finger or toe.

adult_definition: 'To chop away at; to whittle down; to mow down.'
kids_definition: to make or shape something large by cutting
simplified: Cutting a big thing to make it smaller.

adult_definition: 'To commit a crime less serious than a felony.'
kids_definition: to break a law or rule
simplified: If you do something not allowed, you break a rule.

adult_definition: 'To hurt the feelings of; to displease; to make angry; to insult.'
kids_definition: to make somebody feel upset because of something you say or do that is rude or embarrassing
simplified: to upset someone by saying or doing something rude or embarrassing.

adult_definition: 'To distribute objects or pieces of something over an area especially in a random manner.'
kids_definition: to be spread or lying over a surface
simplified: The word "cover" means to put something over a surface, like a thin layer.

adult_definition: 'To distribute objects or pieces of something over an area especially in a random manner.'
kids_definition: to throw or drop things in different directions so that they cover an area of ground
simplified: Scatter things all over the place.

adult_definition: 'To move or swing from side to side; or backward and forward; to rock.'
kids_definition: to move slowly from side to side; to move something in this way
simplified: to sway back and forth.

adult_definition: 'To step or walk (on or over something); to trample.'
kids_definition: to put your foot down while you are stepping or walking
simplified: Put your foot down carefully when walking on soft or uneven ground.

adult_definition: 'A common four-legged animal (Sus scrofa) that has cloven hooves bristles and a nose adapted for digging and is farmed by humans for its meat.'
kids_definition: a male pig that has been castrated (= had part of its sex organs removed) and is kept for its meat
simplified: A special kind of pig that is raised for food.

adult_definition: 'lacking the expected or needed stiffness unleasantly soft.'
kids_definition: not putting enough care attention or energy into something and so not doing it well enough
simplified: Not doing something well because not trying hard enough.

adult_definition: 'Lacking seriousness or earnestness; not in a serious mood.'
kids_definition: that shows a lack of care thought or effort
simplified: The sentence shows that the person did not care or think when speaking or writing.

adult_definition: 'In an abstract state or manner.'
kids_definition: in a way that is based on general ideas and not any particular real person thing or situation
simplified: In a way that is based on ideas and not on real things or situations.

adult_definition: 'A short length of cable used to make an electrical connection or to bypass a circuit.'
kids_definition: a person an animal or an insect that jumps
simplified: An animal that jumps in the air.

adult_definition: 'Given official approval after meeting certain standards.'
kids_definition: officially approved as being of an accepted quality or standard
simplified: Officially approved as very good.

adult_definition: 'To attest to as the truth or meeting a standard.'
kids_definition: to give somebody an official document proving that they are qualified to work in a particular profession
simplified: To give a paper saying someone can do a certain job.

adult_definition: 'The emission of light by a substance that has absorbed light or other electromagnetic radiation.'
kids_definition: bright light produced by some forms of radiation
simplified: Bright light from some kinds of radiation can hurt people.

adult_definition: 'Located in the sea away from the coast.'
kids_definition: blowing from the land towards the sea
simplified: The wind blowing from the land to the sea made a sad sound that seemed to come from the heart of the earth.

adult_definition: 'The result of a computation during which from a large set of data a small figure or few characters are determined that change when the data changes.'
kids_definition: the symbol ( # ) especially one on a phone or computer keyboard
simplified: The symbol ( # ) on a phone or computer keyboard has different names.

adult_definition: 'To impede the movement of (an opponent or a ball).'
kids_definition: to defend yourself against somebody who is attacking you by pushing their arm weapon etc. to one side
simplified: You must defend yourself by moving the attacker's arm and hitting them back.

adult_definition: 'A colleection of persons that were assigend a specific task most often for a predetermined time or to be completed within a given time frame that is to find or determine something make decisions or steer towards a settlement that other are looking for and/or are going to use.'
kids_definition: a group of people with similar interests often within a larger organization or political party
simplified: A group of people with the same likes often belong to a big club or party.

adult_definition: 'Something put around something else usually in order to give it another look or to protect it from its environment.'
kids_definition: an outer layer that covers the surface of a wall to make it look more attractive
simplified: A special layer on a wall makes it look nicer and keeps it safe from rain and sun.

adult_definition: 'Something put around something else usually in order to give it another look or to protect it from its environment.'
kids_definition: a layer of material used to cover the inside surface of something
simplified: A special layer inside something like a pipe or container.

adult_definition: A substance mixed in small quantities with another product to modify its chemical or physical state for example to make food look visually more attractive.
kids_definition: 'a substance that is added in small amounts to something especially food in order to improve it give it colour make it last longer etc.'
simplified: Something added to food to make it better, look nice, and last longer.

adult_definition: An aerosol can for applying paint deodorant etc. as a fine spray.
kids_definition: 'a liquid such as paint or hairspray that is kept under pressure in a metal container and released as a spray'
simplified: 'a spray like paint or hairspray in a metal container'.

adult_definition: The planting of trees in an area or the management of an area to allow trees to regenerate or colonize naturally in order to produce a forest.
kids_definition: 'the process of planting areas of land with trees in order to form a forest'
simplified: 'planting trees to make a forest'.

adult_definition: A channel for supplying water; often underground but treated architecturally on high arches when crossing valleys or low ground.
kids_definition: 'a structure for carrying water usually one built like a bridge across a valley or low ground'
simplified: A bridge carrying water is usually built across a valley.

adult_definition: A group of many islands including the waters that surround them.
kids_definition: 'a group of islands and the sea surrounding them'
simplified: Islands and the sea around them.

adult_definition: The largest phylum in the animal kingdom; adults typically have segmented body a sclerotized integument and many-jointed segmental limbs.
kids_definition: 'an invertebrate animal such as an insect spider or crab that has its skeleton on the outside of its body and has joints on its legs'
simplified: An animal like a spider or crab with a skeleton on the outside and joints on its legs.

adult_definition: A fall or slide of a large mass as of snow or rock down a mountainside.
kids_definition: 'a mass of snow ice and rock that falls down the side of a mountain'
simplified: a large amount of snow, ice, and rock that falls down a mountain side.

adult_definition: An area comprising more than one city and whose boundaries have been designed according to some biological political administrative economic demographic criteria.
kids_definition: 'one of a number of areas that some countries are divided into each with its own local government'
simplified: The country is divided into many areas, each with its own government.

adult_definition: Failure to make payments on time.
kids_definition: 'bad or criminal behaviour usually of young people'
simplified: The bad behaviour of young people is usually criminal.

adult_definition: The statistical study of human vital statistics and population dynamics (natality mortality age profession etc).
kids_definition: 'the changing number of births deaths diseases etc. in a community over a period of time; the scientific study of these changes'
simplified: The number of births, deaths, and diseases in a community changes over time; studying these changes is a science.

adult_definition: Removal of salt and other minerals from water.
kids_definition: 'the process of removing salt from seawater'
simplified: The way to take salt out of seawater.

adult_definition: A wide open comparatively barren tract of land with few forms of life and little rainfall.
kids_definition: 'a large area of land that has very little water and very few plants growing on it. Many deserts are covered by sand.'
simplified: A desert is a big area with little water and few plants. It is often covered in sand.

adult_definition: The act or process of discovering evidence or proof of governmental legal or ethical violations.
kids_definition: 'the process of discovering or noticing something especially something that is not easy to see hear etc.; the fact of being discovered or noticed '
simplified: Finding something, especially when it is hard to see or hear, or being found out.

adult_definition: A surface-active agent used for removing dirt and grease from a variety of surfaces and materials.
kids_definition: 'a liquid or powder that helps remove dirt for example from clothes or dishes'
simplified: Something that helps clean clothes or dishes.

adult_definition: Any measure implement or policy designed to discourage or restrain the actions or advance of another agent organization or state.
kids_definition: 'something that makes somebody less likely to do something (= that deters them)'
simplified: Something that stops someone from doing something.

adult_definition: A method to clean the blood of patients with renal failure.
kids_definition: 'a process for separating substances from a liquid especially for taking waste substances out of the blood of people with damaged kidneys'
simplified: A way to remove bad things from a liquid, especially from people's blood when their kidneys are not working well.

adult_definition: The abode of a human being their place of residence.
kids_definition: 'a house flat etc. where a person lives'
simplified: A house where someone lives.

adult_definition: A river mouth or stream mouth is a part of a river where it flows into the sea river lake reservoir or ocean.
kids_definition: 'the wide part of a river where it flows into the sea'
simplified: 'the big part of a river where it meets the ocean'

adult_definition: Separation of suspended particles from a liquid gas etc. by the action of a filter.
kids_definition: 'the process of filtering a liquid or gas'
simplified: The way of cleaning a liquid or gas.

adult_definition: The art or sport of catching fish with a rod and line and a baited hook or other lure such as a fly.
kids_definition: 'the sport or business of catching fish'
simplified: Catching fish was a big part of the economy of several towns and villages.

adult_definition: A group of persons sharing a home or living space who aggregate and share their incomes as evidenced by the fact that they regularly take meals together.
kids_definition: 'all the people living together in a house or flat'
simplified: All people living in a house.

adult_definition: Earth formed by the decay of vegetable matter.
kids_definition: 'a substance formed from dead leaves and plants that helps plants grow'
simplified: Compost helps plants grow.

adult_definition: The science that treats the occurrence circulation distribution and properties of the waters of the earth and their reaction with the environment.
kids_definition: 'the scientific study of the earth’s water especially its movement in relation to land'
simplified: 'the study of water on earth and how it moves with the land'.

adult_definition: A set of practices associated with the preservation of health the prevention and fighting of diseases and healthy living.
kids_definition: 'the practice of keeping yourself and your living and working areas clean in order to prevent illness and disease'
simplified: keeping yourself and your living and working areas clean helps prevent illness and disease.

adult_definition: Money that a person or an institution obtains.
kids_definition: 'the money that a person a region a country etc. earns from work from investing money from business etc.'
simplified: The money people earn from work, business, and investments.

adult_definition: A breach violation or infringement; as of a law a contract a right or duty.
kids_definition: 'an act of breaking a rule or law'
simplified: 'a wrong thing done on purpose'.

adult_definition: A person occupying a region town house country etc.
kids_definition: 'a person or an animal that lives in a particular place'
simplified: A person or animal that lives somewhere.

adult_definition: An animal with a diet that consists chiefly of insects and similar small creatures.
kids_definition: 'any animal that eats insects'
simplified: Any animal eating insects.

adult_definition: Any animal lacking a backbone including all species not classified as vertebrates.
kids_definition: 'any animal with no backbone for example a worm'
simplified: An animal with no backbone is like a worm.

adult_definition: Higly refined sulphurless kerosene used for kerosene lamps lanterns and portable stoves and produces very little soot.
kids_definition: 'a type of fuel oil that is made from petroleum and that is used in the engines of planes and for heat and light. In British English it is usually called paraffin when it is used for heat and light.'
simplified: Fuel oil comes from petroleum and is used in airplane engines and for heat and light. In British English, it's called paraffin when used for heat and light.

adult_definition: Any reptile of the suborder Lacertilia especially those of the family Lacertidae typically having an elongated body four limbs and a small tail: includes the gechos iguanas chameleons monitors and slow worms.
kids_definition: 'a reptile with a long body and tail four short legs and a rough skin. There are many different types of lizard.'
simplified: A lizard is a reptile with a long body and tail, four short legs, and a rough skin.

adult_definition: One of the most common phyla of animals with over 80000 different described species (of which over 15000 are parasitic). They are ubiquitous in freshwater marine and terrestrial environments where they often outnumber other animals in both individual and species counts and are found in locations as diverse as Antarctica and oceanic trenches.
kids_definition: 'a worm with a thin body that is shaped like a tube and not divided into sections'
simplified: A long worm with a thin body is called an earthworm.

adult_definition: An argument that contradicts what is said by other persons.
kids_definition: 'a reason why you do not like or are opposed to something; a statement about this'
simplified: the reason you do not like something; you say this.

adult_definition: Any activity such as play that diverts amuses or stimulates.
kids_definition: 'the act or process of making something that existed in the past exist or seem to exist again'
simplified: When something from the past comes back to life.

adult_definition: A substance that by undergoing a change in phase (liquid to gas gas to liquid) releases or absorbs a large latent heat in relation to its volume and thus effects a considerable cooling effect.
kids_definition: 'a chemical substance used in the refrigeration process'
simplified: a substance used to cool things.

adult_definition: Any cold-blooded vertebrate of the class Reptilia.
kids_definition: 'any animal that has cold blood and skin covered in scales and that lays eggs. Snakes crocodiles and tortoises are all reptiles.'
simplified: Reptiles are snakes, crocodiles and tortoises.

adult_definition: Scientific investigation aimed at discovering and applying new facts techniques and natural laws.
kids_definition: 'a careful study of a subject especially in order to discover new facts or information about it'
simplified: a careful study to discover new facts about a subject.

adult_definition: An erect grass Oryza sativa that grows in East Asia on wet ground and has drooping flower spikes and yellow oblong edible grains that become white when polished.
kids_definition: 'short narrow white or brown grain grown on wet land in hot countries as food; the plant that produces this grain'
simplified: The rice plant grows in hot countries on wet land to produce white or brown grain as food.

adult_definition: Any amphibian of the order Urodela (or Caudata). The adults keep their tails by opposition to the frogs and the caecilians.
kids_definition: 'an animal like a lizard with short legs and a long tail that is an amphibian (= lives on both land and in water)'
simplified: A lizard-like animal with short legs and a long tail that lives on land and in water.

adult_definition: 1) A legal term referring generally to the act of valuable property being taken into custody by an agent of the court and locked away for safekeeping usually to prevent the property from being disposed of or abused before a dispute over its ownership can be resolved.2) The taking of someone's property voluntarily (by deposit) or involuntarily (by seizure) by court officers or into the possession of a third party awaiting the outcome of a trial in which ownership of that property is at issue.
kids_definition: the act of taking control of somebody's property or assets until a debt has been paid
simplified: When someone owes money, we can take their things until they pay what they owe.

adult_definition: A plant resembling a small tree but has no and will never develop a stem.
kids_definition: 'a large plant that is smaller than a tree and that has several stems of wood coming from the ground'
simplified: a bush is a plant that has several stems of wood coming from the ground.

adult_definition: The inhalation and exhalation of carcinogenic fumes from burning plant material usually tobacco.
kids_definition: 'the activity or habit of smoking cigarettes etc.'
simplified: They looked at the habit of smoking cigarettes again for kids.

adult_definition: Substance generally a liquid capable of dissolving another substance.
kids_definition: 'a substance especially a liquid that can dissolve (= remove or destroy by a chemical process) another substance '
simplified: 'A liquid that can dissolve another substance '

adult_definition: A type of skimmer in the form of a wire mesh basket attached to a handle used to remove food from a hot liquid or skim off foam from a broth.
kids_definition: 'a small creature with eight thin legs. Many spiders spin webs to catch insects for food.'
simplified: There is a small creature with eight thin legs. Many spiders spin webs to catch food.

adult_definition: Fluid or liquid substance that was discharged leaked dripped or running over without control.
kids_definition: 'an act of letting a liquid come or fall out of a container; the amount of liquid that comes or falls out'
simplified: 'pouring out; the amount that pours out'

adult_definition: A sinking down of a part of the earth's crust generally due to underground excavations.
kids_definition: 'the process by which an area of land sinks to a lower level than normal or by which a building sinks into the ground'
simplified: 'the process when the ground goes down or a building falls into it'

adult_definition: The body of specialized words relating to a particular subject.
kids_definition: 'the set of technical words or expressions used in a particular subject'
simplified: 'the special words used in a certain subject'.

adult_definition: Leaves of certain varieties of the tobacco plant cultivated and harvested to make cigarettes cigars snuff for smoking in pipes or for chewing.
kids_definition: 'the dried leaves of the tobacco plant that are used for making cigarettes smoking in a pipe etc.'
simplified: The dry parts of the tobacco plant are used for making cigarettes for smoking.

adult_definition: The loss of water vapour from a plant mainly through the stomata and to a small extent through the cuticle and lenticels.
kids_definition: 'the process of water passing out from the surface of a plant or leaf'
simplified: Water comes out from the surface of a plant or leaf.

adult_definition: The plants that inhabit a certain region or environment.
kids_definition: 'plants in general especially the plants that are found in a particular area or environment'
simplified: Plants, especially those found in a certain place.

adult_definition: A vent in the surface of the Earth through which magma and associated gases and ash erupt.
kids_definition: 'a mountain with a large opening at the top through which gases and lava (= hot liquid rock) are forced out into the air or have been in the past'
simplified: A mountain that shoots out hot liquid rock and gases.

adult_definition: Catching whales to use as food or for their oil etc.
kids_definition: 'the activity or business of hunting and killing whales'
simplified: 'whale hunting' using the following structure: Subject-Object.

adult_definition: A valley especially a long narrow steep valley cut in rock by a river.
kids_definition: 'a deep valley with steep sides of rock'
simplified: A deep valley with steep rocky sides.

adult_definition: Science on education and teaching.
kids_definition: 'the study of teaching methods'
simplified: Learning how to teach is important for schools.

adult_definition: A colorless liquid miscible with water used as a reagent and solvent.
kids_definition: 'the type of alcohol in alcoholic drinks also used as a fuel or solvent'
simplified: Alcohol is used in drinks and as fuel or solvent.

adult_definition: The occupation of taking and printing photographs or making movies.
kids_definition: 'the art process or job of taking photographs or filming something'

adult_definition: Geometrical figure that is circumscribed by straight lines.
